00:00:04.672 --> 00:00:06.674 position:24% line:89% align:start
[triumphant music]

00:00:15.249 --> 00:00:17.752 position:27% line:89% align:start
[mystical music]

00:00:24.191 --> 00:00:26.561 position:30% line:89% align:start
[magical music]

00:00:33.668 --> 00:00:36.036 position:27% line:89% align:start
[wind whistling]

00:00:37.304 --> 00:00:41.576 position:27% line:89% align:start
[harmonica music]

00:00:49.416 --> 00:00:51.184 position:44% line:83% align:start
[man]
 <i>A long, long time ago,</i>

00:00:52.286 --> 00:00:55.188 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>a great catastrophe</i>
 <i>befell heaven and earth.</i>

00:00:58.760 --> 00:01:01.395 position:16% line:5% align:start
 <i>Life hung in the balance</i>

00:01:01.428 --> 00:01:04.131 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>as the world filled with</i>
 <i>violence and destruction.</i>

00:01:06.501 --> 00:01:09.704 position:10% line:5% align:start
 <i>The forces of Shang and Zhou</i>
 <i>fought for supremacy.</i>

00:01:10.304 --> 00:01:13.808 position:13% line:5% align:start
 <i>Humans and gods united to</i>
 <i>get through the catastrophe.</i>

00:01:13.841 --> 00:01:17.444 position:24% line:5% align:start
 <i>And from it came</i>
 <i>the Order of the Gods.</i>

00:01:17.477 --> 00:01:20.213 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Each god returned</i>
 <i>their rightful place,</i>

00:01:20.682 --> 00:01:23.350 position:10% line:5% align:start
 <i>their homes carved in stone.</i>

00:01:23.383 --> 00:01:26.654 position:21% line:5% align:start
 <i>And thus, the world</i>
 <i>returned to peace.</i>

00:01:28.523 --> 00:01:31.693 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:01:48.308 --> 00:01:50.177 position:27% line:89% align:start
[engine hissing]

00:01:54.782 --> 00:01:57.351 position:30% line:89% align:start
[man grunting]

00:01:58.352 --> 00:02:00.588 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:02:05.727 --> 00:02:07.427 position:30% line:89% align:start
[steam hisses]

00:02:08.195 --> 00:02:10.497 position:30% line:89% align:start
[low rumbling]

00:02:19.574 --> 00:02:22.342 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ship rumbling]

00:02:26.948 --> 00:02:29.917 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:02:37.558 --> 00:02:39.627 position:30% line:83% align:start
Hey boss, if we
don't find another job,

00:02:39.661 --> 00:02:40.962 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>we'll be stuck aground!</i>

00:02:40.995 --> 00:02:42.930 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>That's the last</i>
 <i>of the Cosmic Gas!</i>

00:02:45.900 --> 00:02:48.235 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

00:02:52.239 --> 00:02:53.440 position:27% line:89% align:start
We need the work.

00:02:53.473 --> 00:02:54.842 position:10% line:89% align:start
How long since the last gig?

00:02:54.876 --> 00:02:56.844 position:24% line:83% align:start
Can't get gas with
no money left.

00:03:01.448 --> 00:03:02.750 position:33% line:89% align:start
[dog barking]

00:03:02.784 --> 00:03:04.585 position:33% line:89% align:start
Isn't it sad?

00:03:04.619 --> 00:03:06.621 position:16% line:83% align:start
Immortals and demons used
to dance in the clouds.

00:03:07.320 --> 00:03:08.623 position:5% line:89% align:start
Since then, we've fallen so low.

00:03:08.990 --> 00:03:10.525 position:19% line:89% align:start
Even the birds mock us.

00:03:11.759 --> 00:03:13.561 position:10% line:83% align:start
Flying boats is all we've got
since that damn catastrophe.

00:03:14.762 --> 00:03:16.263 position:19% line:89% align:start
How long ago was that?

00:03:16.531 --> 00:03:17.598 position:21% line:89% align:start
You remember exactly?

00:03:20.367 --> 00:03:22.402 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Long ago.
-[man] Too true.

00:03:22.436 --> 00:03:24.572 position:7% line:89% align:start
Do I even remember how to fly?

00:03:24.605 --> 00:03:27.542 position:19% line:83% align:start
Just thinking about it
feels like a fantasy, huh?

00:03:27.575 --> 00:03:29.811 position:30% line:89% align:start
[bell ringing]

00:03:36.517 --> 00:03:38.653 position:33% line:89% align:start
[dog barking]

00:03:43.958 --> 00:03:45.660 position:44% line:83% align:start
Hey!
Well would you look at that!

00:03:45.860 --> 00:03:47.829 position:13% line:89% align:start
Oh! A request from Penglai!

00:03:48.730 --> 00:03:50.263 position:13% line:89% align:start
Home of the gods, Penglai?

00:03:50.297 --> 00:03:51.866 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's our lucky day!

00:03:51.899 --> 00:03:54.769 position:13% line:83% align:start
Ha! We'll get there before
any other bounty hunter can.

00:03:56.671 --> 00:03:58.873 position:21% line:89% align:start
Come on, only 20,000?

00:04:01.441 --> 00:04:04.512 position:24% line:83% align:start
A guy this ruthless
should be twice as much.

00:04:04.545 --> 00:04:05.847 position:13% line:89% align:start
Do the gods have no money?

00:04:06.581 --> 00:04:09.751 position:19% line:83% align:start
If we don't find work,
we won't eat either.

00:04:20.427 --> 00:04:21.863 position:30% line:83% align:start
May as well go
try our luck, then.

00:04:23.698 --> 00:04:24.899 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whimpers]

00:04:29.369 --> 00:04:33.875 position:30% line:83% align:start
[ship rumbling]
[smooth music]

00:05:07.608 --> 00:05:08.709 position:41% line:89% align:start
[thuds]

00:05:12.647 --> 00:05:14.615 position:27% line:5% align:start
[music continues]

00:05:15.650 --> 00:05:17.118 position:30% line:5% align:start
[woman over PA]
 <i>The morning cycle had ended.</i>

00:05:17.151 --> 00:05:19.419 position:27% line:5% align:start
 <i>The Zhuque Gate</i>
 <i>is now open</i>

00:05:19.452 --> 00:05:21.388 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>for travelers to pass through.</i>

00:05:21.421 --> 00:05:23.925 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>You are entering Penglai.</i>

00:05:23.958 --> 00:05:26.527 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>We welcome gods and spirits.</i>

00:05:26.561 --> 00:05:29.931 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>May you be blessed with</i>
 <i>security and prosperity</i>

00:05:29.964 --> 00:05:33.000 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>so long as you</i>
 <i>comply by the rules.</i>

00:05:33.034 --> 00:05:36.070 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:05:42.176 --> 00:05:45.046 position:19% line:89% align:start
[indistinct chattering]

00:05:48.182 --> 00:05:49.984 position:30% line:89% align:start
[steam hissing]

00:06:01.629 --> 00:06:03.898 position:21% line:89% align:start
[footsteps thudding]

00:06:08.936 --> 00:06:11.672 position:24% line:89% align:start
[harmonica playing]

00:06:20.815 --> 00:06:22.683 position:10% line:89% align:start
You want the elixir of life?

00:06:22.717 --> 00:06:25.418 position:27% line:83% align:start
Show me the cash,
or move it along.

00:06:27.521 --> 00:06:28.923 position:13% line:89% align:start
The goods are counterfeit.

00:06:28.956 --> 00:06:30.157 position:30% line:89% align:start
Then walk away.

00:06:32.526 --> 00:06:35.196 position:16% line:89% align:start
One immortal, one demon.

00:06:35.229 --> 00:06:36.564 position:16% line:89% align:start
You make quite the pair.

00:06:37.497 --> 00:06:40.167 position:24% line:83% align:start
You do what you can
when times are tough.

00:06:40.735 --> 00:06:43.037 position:13% line:83% align:start
Better a dog than a washed
up god, don't you think?

00:06:43.938 --> 00:06:45.106 position:41% line:89% align:start
Maybe.

00:06:45.673 --> 00:06:47.407 position:10% line:89% align:start
My dog's got it pretty easy.

00:06:49.110 --> 00:06:50.511 position:38% line:89% align:start
See that?

00:06:50.544 --> 00:06:51.612 position:19% line:89% align:start
I even smell like her.

00:07:05.660 --> 00:07:06.493 position:27% line:89% align:start
You're my bounty.

00:07:10.131 --> 00:07:11.899 position:16% line:89% align:start
[scoffs] You kidding me?

00:07:11.933 --> 00:07:14.168 position:24% line:83% align:start
I thought you were
a sheriff or something.

00:07:14.201 --> 00:07:17.071 position:16% line:83% align:start
Turns out you're nothing
but a little bounty hunter.

00:07:17.705 --> 00:07:18.873 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:07:18.906 --> 00:07:20.440 position:35% line:89% align:start
[crashing]

00:07:20.875 --> 00:07:21.876 position:27% line:89% align:start
[inhaling deeply]

00:07:23.611 --> 00:07:25.713 position:30% line:89% align:start
[intense music]

00:07:32.653 --> 00:07:33.721 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ax thuds]

00:07:40.828 --> 00:07:42.063 position:33% line:89% align:start
[loud thump]

00:07:42.096 --> 00:07:43.531 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:07:46.067 --> 00:07:48.836 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:07:48.869 --> 00:07:50.171 position:19% line:89% align:start
Talk about a hard head.

00:07:52.006 --> 00:07:53.841 position:30% line:89% align:start
[upbeat music]

00:07:55.009 --> 00:07:56.243 position:16% line:89% align:start
Hey, why are you running?

00:07:57.044 --> 00:07:58.512 position:16% line:89% align:start
I just want the bounty.

00:08:01.015 --> 00:08:02.583 position:30% line:89% align:start
Careful! Wait!

00:08:02.616 --> 00:08:05.152 position:24% line:89% align:start
[items clattering]

00:08:06.821 --> 00:08:08.889 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:08:10.324 --> 00:08:12.693 position:30% line:5% align:start
[vehicle revs]
[water splashing]

00:08:19.233 --> 00:08:20.101 position:35% line:89% align:start
[boy gasps]

00:08:28.042 --> 00:08:29.143 position:30% line:89% align:start
[bridge cracks]

00:08:31.579 --> 00:08:33.514 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:08:36.083 --> 00:08:37.084 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yelps]

00:08:37.818 --> 00:08:38.786 position:30% line:89% align:start
[wood crashing]

00:08:38.819 --> 00:08:39.854 position:30% line:89% align:start
Hey! Watch it!

00:08:45.292 --> 00:08:46.527 position:30% line:89% align:start
[horns honking]

00:08:48.829 --> 00:08:49.764 position:30% line:89% align:start
[orbs bubbling]

00:08:50.231 --> 00:08:51.565 position:33% line:89% align:start
[explosions]

00:08:55.970 --> 00:08:57.238 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:08:57.271 --> 00:08:58.539 position:27% line:89% align:start
[people shouting]

00:09:02.877 --> 00:09:04.545 position:30% line:89% align:start
[boy grunting]

00:09:12.253 --> 00:09:15.056 position:27% line:89% align:start
[birds squawking]

00:09:19.260 --> 00:09:21.295 position:30% line:89% align:start
[meter beeping]

00:09:25.633 --> 00:09:27.068 position:30% line:89% align:start
[engine booms]

00:09:30.671 --> 00:09:31.705 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:09:37.278 --> 00:09:38.179 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ship rattling]

00:09:40.748 --> 00:09:42.183 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ship sputtering]

00:09:43.284 --> 00:09:45.252 position:35% line:83% align:start
Out of gas.
That's just perfect.

00:09:47.154 --> 00:09:49.590 position:24% line:89% align:start
See ya around! Ha!

00:09:49.924 --> 00:09:51.192 position:30% line:89% align:start
[net whooshes]

00:09:52.059 --> 00:09:55.196 position:38% line:83% align:start
[groans]
You've got to be kidding me.

00:09:55.796 --> 00:09:56.630 position:27% line:89% align:start
[loud thud]

00:09:57.965 --> 00:09:59.066 position:33% line:89% align:start
Good timing.

00:09:59.767 --> 00:10:00.968 position:27% line:89% align:start
It wasn't timing.

00:10:01.001 --> 00:10:02.736 position:27% line:89% align:start
It was her nose.

00:10:02.770 --> 00:10:05.139 position:21% line:83% align:start
She found you pretty
quickly using your scent.

00:10:05.172 --> 00:10:07.942 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Xiaotian grunting]

00:10:09.176 --> 00:10:11.345 position:21% line:89% align:start
You're back! [laughs]

00:10:11.378 --> 00:10:13.814 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Xiaotian shouting]
[both grunting]

00:10:14.982 --> 00:10:16.984 position:30% line:83% align:start
-That's enough.
-What is that?

00:10:17.017 --> 00:10:18.185 position:19% line:89% align:start
What an embarrassment.

00:10:20.054 --> 00:10:21.288 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Xiaotian growls]

00:10:21.722 --> 00:10:24.091 position:38% line:83% align:start
Say what?
Are you jealous or something?

00:10:24.125 --> 00:10:25.759 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Help me!
-You want your money, right?

00:10:25.793 --> 00:10:28.395 position:19% line:83% align:start
Let me go and I'll pay
you five times the reward.

00:10:28.929 --> 00:10:30.431 position:24% line:89% align:start
100 grand! [grunts]

00:10:30.464 --> 00:10:32.099 position:33% line:83% align:start
Do you expect
us to believe you?

00:10:32.700 --> 00:10:34.201 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Seriously?
-It's true. Really.

00:10:34.235 --> 00:10:35.669 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's buried by the bridge.

00:10:35.703 --> 00:10:36.804 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'll show you where it's.

00:10:38.272 --> 00:10:40.274 position:7% line:89% align:start
Hey, that's a pretty good deal.

00:10:42.710 --> 00:10:44.145 position:13% line:89% align:start
Well then, heads or tails?

00:10:45.746 --> 00:10:46.914 position:16% line:89% align:start
What do you mean by that?

00:10:47.882 --> 00:10:49.984 position:27% line:83% align:start
Why don't we let
the cosmos decide?

00:10:50.017 --> 00:10:51.719 position:16% line:89% align:start
Do I set you free or not?

00:10:51.752 --> 00:10:52.386 position:35% line:89% align:start
Sound good?

00:10:53.721 --> 00:10:54.755 position:33% line:89% align:start
Mm-hm, mm-hm.

00:10:57.057 --> 00:10:59.293 position:30% line:89% align:start
[upbeat music]

00:11:01.428 --> 00:11:02.796 position:33% line:89% align:start
[whimpering]

00:11:04.064 --> 00:11:04.965 position:27% line:89% align:start
[man] 20 strings.

00:11:07.735 --> 00:11:10.104 position:30% line:89% align:start
[men grunting]

00:11:16.310 --> 00:11:19.013 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hey, boss, when you did
the heads or tails thing,

00:11:19.046 --> 00:11:21.949 position:7% line:83% align:start
was it heads up you let him go
or heads down you let him go?

00:11:21.982 --> 00:11:23.150 position:19% line:89% align:start
You didn't really say.

00:11:23.184 --> 00:11:26.153 position:24% line:89% align:start
[creature growling]

00:11:28.255 --> 00:11:30.958 position:30% line:89% align:start
[smooth music]

00:11:33.460 --> 00:11:34.295 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yelps]

00:11:37.331 --> 00:11:40.367 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Xiaotian panting, yelping]

00:11:41.869 --> 00:11:43.237 position:30% line:89% align:start
Enough. Enough.

00:11:43.837 --> 00:11:44.872 position:41% line:89% align:start
Money!

00:11:45.906 --> 00:11:47.208 position:38% line:89% align:start
Visitor.

00:11:47.241 --> 00:11:48.309 position:19% line:89% align:start
Must be a new customer.

00:11:48.342 --> 00:11:51.513 position:38% line:83% align:start
Oh yeah!
And she's really cute!

00:11:51.546 --> 00:11:53.280 position:13% line:89% align:start
[laughing] Pretty! Pretty!

00:11:53.314 --> 00:11:54.381 position:13% line:89% align:start
Wonder what she's here for.

00:11:59.220 --> 00:12:00.321 position:30% line:89% align:start
Are you Erlang?

00:12:03.357 --> 00:12:05.759 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's Mu. Mu Erlang.

00:12:05.793 --> 00:12:06.427 position:35% line:89% align:start
That's me.

00:12:07.361 --> 00:12:08.862 position:19% line:89% align:start
There's someone I seek.

00:12:08.896 --> 00:12:11.298 position:30% line:83% align:start
Hey, my men and
I are bounty hunters.

00:12:11.332 --> 00:12:13.801 position:27% line:83% align:start
We catch people.
We don't find them.

00:12:14.134 --> 00:12:15.903 position:10% line:83% align:start
[exhales sharply] I need you
to catch someone then.

00:12:15.936 --> 00:12:17.204 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:12:17.438 --> 00:12:18.372 position:7% line:89% align:start
Now that's something I can do.

00:12:19.907 --> 00:12:22.243 position:5% line:83% align:start
He stole something from me.
It was my sister's.

00:12:22.577 --> 00:12:23.410 position:27% line:89% align:start
And what was it?

00:12:26.280 --> 00:12:27.448 position:21% line:89% align:start
No. I shouldn't say.

00:12:28.415 --> 00:12:30.317 position:24% line:89% align:start
[scoffs] All right.

00:12:31.118 --> 00:12:32.386 position:24% line:89% align:start
That's fine by me.

00:12:32.419 --> 00:12:33.420 position:13% line:89% align:start
Less for me to worry about.

00:12:35.189 --> 00:12:37.024 position:7% line:89% align:start
Don't share. Keep your secrets.

00:12:39.860 --> 00:12:40.894 position:38% line:89% align:start
Thirsty?

00:12:42.564 --> 00:12:44.965 position:27% line:83% align:start
My sister and I,
we were very close.

00:12:46.467 --> 00:12:49.003 position:19% line:83% align:start
But during the upheaval
12 years ago, she disappeared.

00:12:50.838 --> 00:12:53.307 position:16% line:83% align:start
The item that he stole is
all that's left of her.

00:12:55.042 --> 00:12:56.578 position:27% line:89% align:start
Will you help me?

00:12:56.611 --> 00:12:58.312 position:35% line:83% align:start
I can help.
There's a fee though.

00:13:06.320 --> 00:13:08.422 position:13% line:89% align:start
This is my offer. Take it.

00:13:10.991 --> 00:13:13.294 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Xiaotian grunting]

00:13:27.441 --> 00:13:30.210 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Wanluo coughing]

00:13:33.314 --> 00:13:35.015 position:35% line:89% align:start
All right.

00:13:35.049 --> 00:13:35.849 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'll tell you.

00:13:36.917 --> 00:13:38.152 position:7% line:89% align:start
It's called the Lamp of Wishes.

00:13:40.087 --> 00:13:42.222 position:21% line:83% align:start
It has the ability to
contain things that otherwise

00:13:42.256 --> 00:13:43.290 position:27% line:89% align:start
cannot be bound.

00:13:44.458 --> 00:13:46.126 position:33% line:89% align:start
A rare power.

00:13:46.160 --> 00:13:48.128 position:30% line:83% align:start
I tracked it to
Fang Hu Xian Island.

00:13:48.362 --> 00:13:51.365 position:21% line:83% align:start
So the one you seek,
he must have a name, right?

00:13:51.398 --> 00:13:52.466 position:35% line:89% align:start
Chenxiang.

00:13:53.267 --> 00:13:54.502 position:35% line:89% align:start
Chenxiang.

00:13:54.536 --> 00:13:56.170 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's right.

00:13:56.203 --> 00:13:57.037 position:27% line:89% align:start
Do you know him?

00:13:59.473 --> 00:14:01.041 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's a unique name.

00:14:01.241 --> 00:14:04.411 position:21% line:89% align:start
[propellers whirring]

00:14:06.313 --> 00:14:08.916 position:10% line:89% align:start
Hey! We never got your name!

00:14:08.949 --> 00:14:11.385 position:33% line:83% align:start
It's Wanluo.
I'll be waiting in Yingzhou.

00:14:15.022 --> 00:14:16.256 position:33% line:89% align:start
[horn blows]

00:14:17.191 --> 00:14:18.292 position:19% line:89% align:start
There's a story there.

00:14:18.325 --> 00:14:20.461 position:16% line:89% align:start
Oh yeah, that's for sure.

00:14:20.494 --> 00:14:22.229 position:27% line:83% align:start
Look at her gown,
and also her ship,

00:14:22.262 --> 00:14:23.864 position:13% line:89% align:start
and her exquisite manners.

00:14:25.232 --> 00:14:27.468 position:10% line:89% align:start
But why would she come to us?

00:14:27.502 --> 00:14:28.969 position:7% line:89% align:start
Other than being the cheapest,

00:14:29.604 --> 00:14:31.105 position:24% line:83% align:start
we don't have much
going for us.

00:14:33.641 --> 00:14:35.677 position:30% line:5% align:start
[woman over PA]
 <i>On sale for the next 15 days</i>

00:14:35.710 --> 00:14:38.011 position:21% line:5% align:start
 <i>while supplies last,</i>

00:14:38.379 --> 00:14:42.449 position:10% line:5% align:start
 <i>the highest quality fuel for</i>
 <i>the highest quality flying.</i>

00:14:42.650 --> 00:14:45.185 position:35% line:83% align:start
Next order:
three bags of Cosmic Gas.

00:14:45.653 --> 00:14:47.955 position:13% line:89% align:start
Collect it over there, sir.

00:14:47.988 --> 00:14:48.422 position:41% line:83% align:start
[girl]
Three bags coming right up!

00:14:50.124 --> 00:14:52.893 position:24% line:89% align:start
[machines whirring]

00:15:00.334 --> 00:15:02.302 position:33% line:89% align:start
[whip cracks]

00:15:04.606 --> 00:15:08.942 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:15:24.592 --> 00:15:26.093 position:10% line:89% align:start
[man] All right. Move along.

00:15:26.126 --> 00:15:28.195 position:30% line:5% align:start
[woman over PA]
 <i>On sale for the next 15 days</i>

00:15:28.228 --> 00:15:29.463 position:21% line:5% align:start
 <i>while supplies last,</i>

00:15:30.865 --> 00:15:34.101 position:10% line:5% align:start
 <i>the highest quality fuel for</i>
 <i>the highest quality flying.</i>

00:15:35.302 --> 00:15:36.470 position:30% line:89% align:start
[smooth music]

00:15:37.772 --> 00:15:39.206 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunts]
-Watch it!

00:15:40.140 --> 00:15:41.676 position:21% line:83% align:start
-[creatures grunting]
-No need to fight!

00:15:41.709 --> 00:15:43.043 position:24% line:89% align:start
Someone stop them!

00:15:43.645 --> 00:15:44.546 position:5% line:89% align:start
Knock it off! Both of you!

00:15:45.446 --> 00:15:46.581 position:33% line:89% align:start
You hear me?

00:15:46.614 --> 00:15:48.248 position:30% line:89% align:start
[upbeat music]

00:15:50.350 --> 00:15:51.719 position:21% line:89% align:start
No fighting allowed!

00:15:51.753 --> 00:15:53.153 position:27% line:89% align:start
What's going on?

00:15:53.187 --> 00:15:55.255 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:16:03.130 --> 00:16:05.065 position:30% line:89% align:start
[guard grunts]

00:16:17.745 --> 00:16:20.548 position:27% line:89% align:start
[guards grunting]

00:16:28.155 --> 00:16:30.290 position:30% line:83% align:start
[metal creaks]
[growls]

00:16:30.324 --> 00:16:33.060 position:35% line:83% align:start
Unhand me!
Let go of me, you ugly brute!

00:16:33.828 --> 00:16:34.662 position:30% line:89% align:start
Out of my way!

00:16:35.496 --> 00:16:36.664 position:30% line:89% align:start
And stay down.

00:16:39.466 --> 00:16:40.668 position:30% line:89% align:start
[man] Let's go!

00:16:40.702 --> 00:16:42.570 position:16% line:89% align:start
What are looking at? Huh?

00:16:45.305 --> 00:16:46.508 position:33% line:89% align:start
[whip cracks]

00:16:48.108 --> 00:16:51.478 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

00:16:57.417 --> 00:16:59.286 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:17:22.677 --> 00:17:24.546 position:41% line:83% align:start
[yells]
[creature groaning]

00:17:25.747 --> 00:17:28.348 position:21% line:89% align:start
[creature grumbling]

00:17:30.552 --> 00:17:31.819 position:33% line:89% align:start
[body thuds]

00:17:33.420 --> 00:17:35.188 position:21% line:83% align:start
[creatures squealing]
[shushes]

00:17:37.792 --> 00:17:40.762 position:30% line:89% align:start
[smooth music]

00:17:41.495 --> 00:17:44.131 position:27% line:89% align:start
[metal clicking]

00:18:03.383 --> 00:18:05.553 position:30% line:83% align:start
[drums beating]
[gasps]

00:18:05.587 --> 00:18:06.854 position:19% line:89% align:start
[creatures whimpering]

00:18:07.387 --> 00:18:09.691 position:10% line:83% align:start
[gasps] Boss! Heaven's Army!
[grunts]

00:18:09.724 --> 00:18:11.358 position:19% line:89% align:start
Who sounded the alarm?

00:18:11.391 --> 00:18:14.094 position:30% line:83% align:start
[drums beating]
[ships whirring]

00:18:15.262 --> 00:18:16.296 position:38% line:89% align:start
Let's go!

00:18:17.297 --> 00:18:19.166 position:30% line:89% align:start
[all grunting]

00:18:21.636 --> 00:18:23.805 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

00:18:25.506 --> 00:18:26.641 position:35% line:89% align:start
Over there!

00:18:28.576 --> 00:18:29.577 position:21% line:89% align:start
You there, that way!

00:18:31.345 --> 00:18:33.347 position:5% line:89% align:start
[soldiers shouting indistinctly]

00:18:36.283 --> 00:18:37.619 position:33% line:89% align:start
[whimpering]

00:18:39.419 --> 00:18:41.723 position:30% line:89% align:start
[upbeat music]

00:18:43.223 --> 00:18:44.424 position:27% line:89% align:start
Get to the boat.

00:18:44.458 --> 00:18:46.794 position:30% line:89% align:start
[all shouting]

00:18:49.897 --> 00:18:52.466 position:33% line:89% align:start
[screeching]

00:18:52.499 --> 00:18:54.636 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:19:07.414 --> 00:19:08.583 position:30% line:89% align:start
Help me, boss!

00:19:13.821 --> 00:19:15.288 position:27% line:89% align:start
[soldiers groan]

00:19:22.630 --> 00:19:23.765 position:16% line:89% align:start
[soldier] Come back here!

00:19:24.832 --> 00:19:26.433 position:16% line:83% align:start
[boss] Start the engine!
Start the engine!

00:19:29.436 --> 00:19:31.405 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hey! Wait for me!

00:19:31.438 --> 00:19:32.674 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Little brat!
-Halt!

00:19:38.513 --> 00:19:39.881 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:19:39.914 --> 00:19:43.584 position:24% line:89% align:start
[grunting, yelling]

00:19:55.362 --> 00:19:57.732 position:27% line:5% align:start
[ethereal music]

00:20:08.876 --> 00:20:11.612 position:27% line:89% align:start
[rings whirring]

00:20:19.520 --> 00:20:20.822 position:24% line:89% align:start
Ready for take off!

00:20:21.823 --> 00:20:22.990 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yelps]

00:20:23.524 --> 00:20:25.492 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:20:26.994 --> 00:20:28.863 position:30% line:83% align:start
[woman over PA]
 <i>Initialization complete.</i>

00:20:28.896 --> 00:20:32.734 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>The next station is Fang Hu.</i>

00:20:32.767 --> 00:20:35.302 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>Arrival time, 7:45 PM.</i>

00:20:35.503 --> 00:20:37.905 position:7% line:83% align:start
[woman continues indistinctly]
[Xiaotian cheering]

00:20:37.939 --> 00:20:38.906 position:30% line:83% align:start
[woman over PA]
 <i>Have a safe journey.</i>

00:20:40.775 --> 00:20:43.511 position:21% line:89% align:start
[light upbeat music]

00:21:02.429 --> 00:21:03.798 position:16% line:89% align:start
Ah. Hello. Welcome, sir.

00:21:05.066 --> 00:21:07.034 position:30% line:83% align:start
Come. This way.
This way, please.

00:21:08.870 --> 00:21:10.772 position:27% line:83% align:start
He's got no money
left to play with.

00:21:10.805 --> 00:21:11.839 position:38% line:89% align:start
Beat it!

00:21:13.941 --> 00:21:16.611 position:30% line:89% align:start
[upbeat music]

00:21:31.659 --> 00:21:32.827 position:27% line:89% align:start
Place your bets!

00:21:32.860 --> 00:21:33.895 position:35% line:89% align:start
Here we go!

00:21:38.398 --> 00:21:40.034 position:24% line:89% align:start
Erlang! [laughing]

00:21:40.067 --> 00:21:41.468 position:21% line:89% align:start
Erlang, you're back!

00:21:42.637 --> 00:21:44.005 position:38% line:89% align:start
Hi, Cal.

00:21:44.038 --> 00:21:45.438 position:44% line:83% align:start
[Cal]
So, what can I get for you?

00:21:45.472 --> 00:21:46.874 position:33% line:89% align:start
Information.

00:21:46.908 --> 00:21:49.577 position:19% line:83% align:start
Oh, gee, these old ears
don't hear so well these days.

00:21:49.877 --> 00:21:51.344 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yelping]

00:21:51.378 --> 00:21:53.714 position:24% line:83% align:start
Even deaf, you hear
better than most.

00:21:54.015 --> 00:21:55.583 position:7% line:89% align:start
[whimpers, chuckles nervously]

00:21:56.017 --> 00:21:57.952 position:10% line:89% align:start
I guess I do owe you a favor.

00:21:57.985 --> 00:21:58.920 position:35% line:83% align:start
[whispers]
What do you want to know?

00:21:59.787 --> 00:22:01.055 position:24% line:83% align:start
Looking for someone
named Chenxiang.

00:22:01.088 --> 00:22:02.657 position:30% line:89% align:start
Huh? Chenxiang?

00:22:03.825 --> 00:22:05.092 position:16% line:89% align:start
I've never heard of him.

00:22:11.766 --> 00:22:13.034 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'll be going now!

00:22:13.634 --> 00:22:14.669 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hey!

00:22:15.903 --> 00:22:17.972 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:22:19.607 --> 00:22:20.440 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hello, you three.

00:22:22.143 --> 00:22:24.979 position:7% line:89% align:start
[chuckles] What a surprise. Ha!

00:22:28.049 --> 00:22:29.650 position:7% line:89% align:start
Let me get a good look at you.

00:22:30.051 --> 00:22:31.619 position:27% line:89% align:start
[chuckling]

00:22:33.453 --> 00:22:34.622 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah.

00:22:37.758 --> 00:22:39.627 position:24% line:89% align:start
Oh, hey, hey, hey.

00:22:39.894 --> 00:22:40.862 position:19% line:89% align:start
Now what was that for?

00:22:45.833 --> 00:22:46.968 position:41% line:89% align:start
Blind!

00:22:47.001 --> 00:22:48.435 position:24% line:89% align:start
So it's true then.

00:22:49.837 --> 00:22:53.074 position:16% line:89% align:start
[giggles] Oh, Mu Erlang.

00:22:53.774 --> 00:22:56.409 position:19% line:89% align:start
Bounty hunter now, no?

00:22:56.443 --> 00:22:58.646 position:27% line:83% align:start
Listen, sir, no,
no, no, no, no, no.

00:22:58.679 --> 00:23:00.081 position:38% line:89% align:start
Brother.

00:23:00.114 --> 00:23:02.683 position:19% line:83% align:start
Wait a second, where's
your three-headed sword?

00:23:02.717 --> 00:23:05.853 position:19% line:83% align:start
And your silver-bullet
slingshot, huh?

00:23:05.887 --> 00:23:07.688 position:27% line:89% align:start
They're all gone?

00:23:07.722 --> 00:23:09.824 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:23:09.857 --> 00:23:12.960 position:13% line:83% align:start
Ladies and gentlemen, gaze
upon the great and once mighty

00:23:12.994 --> 00:23:14.829 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yang Jian.

00:23:15.062 --> 00:23:16.831 position:16% line:83% align:start
[woman] Is it really him?
It can't be.

00:23:16.864 --> 00:23:17.732 position:44% line:83% align:start
[man]
What happened to him?

00:23:17.765 --> 00:23:19.432 position:30% line:89% align:start
Good question.

00:23:19.466 --> 00:23:21.202 position:19% line:89% align:start
What did happen to you?

00:23:21.235 --> 00:23:24.038 position:27% line:83% align:start
Hey, don't worry,
why don't I tell them?

00:23:25.472 --> 00:23:26.941 position:33% line:83% align:start
[hollow thud]
[clearing throat]

00:23:26.974 --> 00:23:30.111 position:13% line:89% align:start
Years ago, 12 to be exact,

00:23:30.144 --> 00:23:33.014 position:16% line:83% align:start
a goddess by the name of
Yang Chan had the gall

00:23:33.047 --> 00:23:34.916 position:30% line:83% align:start
to fall in love
with a mortal human,

00:23:34.949 --> 00:23:36.784 position:19% line:89% align:start
breaking Heaven's laws.

00:23:36.817 --> 00:23:40.054 position:21% line:83% align:start
So Yang Jian trapped
her under Mount Hua.

00:23:41.488 --> 00:23:43.758 position:7% line:89% align:start
And she's his sister by blood.

00:23:43.791 --> 00:23:46.127 position:21% line:89% align:start
[patrons whispering]

00:23:46.594 --> 00:23:49.196 position:19% line:83% align:start
But Yang Chan would not
be trapped so easily.

00:23:49.230 --> 00:23:53.067 position:13% line:83% align:start
She fought back hard, using
Mount Hua's legendary Lotus Lamp

00:23:53.100 --> 00:23:56.637 position:19% line:83% align:start
to blind his Third Eye,
impairing his abilities.

00:23:56.671 --> 00:24:00.074 position:10% line:83% align:start
Since then, the powerful Yang
Jian hasn't been able to use

00:24:00.107 --> 00:24:02.009 position:35% line:89% align:start
his powers.

00:24:02.043 --> 00:24:03.077 position:19% line:89% align:start
[man] Serves him right!

00:24:04.011 --> 00:24:05.846 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh, why?

00:24:05.880 --> 00:24:10.584 position:10% line:83% align:start
So I ask, what kind of person
would be such a rule follower

00:24:10.851 --> 00:24:13.721 position:21% line:83% align:start
they'd seal their own
sister under a mountain?

00:24:13.754 --> 00:24:15.923 position:21% line:83% align:start
His actions left the
marriage destroyed,

00:24:15.957 --> 00:24:17.892 position:21% line:89% align:start
and a family in ruin!

00:24:17.925 --> 00:24:21.128 position:27% line:89% align:start
[monkey laughing]

00:24:21.629 --> 00:24:24.765 position:16% line:83% align:start
Yang Jian, do you recall
the day you arrested

00:24:24.799 --> 00:24:25.833 position:27% line:89% align:start
the three of us?

00:24:25.866 --> 00:24:27.535 position:30% line:89% align:start
All that power.

00:24:28.703 --> 00:24:32.173 position:24% line:83% align:start
Today I can finally
pay you back for that.

00:24:35.276 --> 00:24:37.545 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

00:24:38.913 --> 00:24:40.548 position:30% line:89% align:start
[loud crashing]

00:24:44.585 --> 00:24:46.153 position:13% line:89% align:start
Let's keep it rolling then!

00:24:47.621 --> 00:24:50.758 position:13% line:89% align:start
[chuckles nervously, yelps]

00:24:51.926 --> 00:24:53.995 position:19% line:89% align:start
Two of the Mo Brothers.

00:24:54.028 --> 00:24:56.063 position:21% line:89% align:start
Mo Lihong. Mo Lihai.

00:24:57.098 --> 00:24:59.800 position:38% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:25:00.101 --> 00:25:02.169 position:27% line:89% align:start
[crowd muttering]

00:25:04.939 --> 00:25:08.776 position:35% line:83% align:start
[laughing]
So it's true. Hey, Yang Jian.

00:25:08.809 --> 00:25:10.878 position:16% line:83% align:start
I never would've imagined
that one day I'd be the one

00:25:10.911 --> 00:25:12.179 position:35% line:89% align:start
saving you.

00:25:12.680 --> 00:25:14.148 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Jian chuckles]

00:25:14.181 --> 00:25:16.884 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Lihong] You've kept a pretty
low profile these last 12 years.

00:25:17.284 --> 00:25:19.754 position:30% line:83% align:start
Ever since the
Mount Hua incident.

00:25:20.654 --> 00:25:23.257 position:21% line:83% align:start
And you really became
a bounty hunter, I see.

00:25:23.290 --> 00:25:25.059 position:27% line:89% align:start
One needs to eat.

00:25:25.359 --> 00:25:27.194 position:13% line:89% align:start
You're looking for someone.

00:25:27.228 --> 00:25:28.863 position:24% line:83% align:start
I heard you mention
a name earlier.

00:25:29.697 --> 00:25:31.632 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Oh, the bounty.
-The guy's ours!

00:25:31.899 --> 00:25:34.168 position:7% line:89% align:start
We're both after the same man.

00:25:34.201 --> 00:25:37.071 position:13% line:83% align:start
I suggest you let this go,
for your sake.

00:25:37.104 --> 00:25:39.673 position:19% line:83% align:start
[laughs] Are you really
threatening Yang Jian?

00:25:39.707 --> 00:25:41.075 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Lihai laughing]

00:25:41.108 --> 00:25:44.078 position:10% line:83% align:start
Yang Jian, you are definitely
not the same guy, huh?

00:25:44.111 --> 00:25:45.179 position:30% line:89% align:start
See you around.

00:25:45.212 --> 00:25:47.948 position:24% line:89% align:start
[soft guitar music]

00:25:52.953 --> 00:25:55.623 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Jian whistling]

00:25:58.025 --> 00:25:59.326 position:21% line:89% align:start
[man] Come back here!

00:25:59.360 --> 00:26:01.228 position:27% line:89% align:start
[mystical music]

00:26:05.766 --> 00:26:07.568 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Move it!
-[panting]

00:26:08.269 --> 00:26:09.336 position:16% line:89% align:start
[man] You won't get away!

00:26:12.273 --> 00:26:13.307 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:26:14.408 --> 00:26:16.177 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

00:26:17.711 --> 00:26:19.013 position:27% line:89% align:start
[thugs laughing]

00:26:19.713 --> 00:26:21.816 position:30% line:89% align:start
[yawns, yelps]

00:26:21.849 --> 00:26:23.050 position:27% line:89% align:start
[water splashing]

00:26:29.223 --> 00:26:31.926 position:21% line:83% align:start
Were you naive enough
to think that you can run

00:26:31.959 --> 00:26:33.060 position:30% line:89% align:start
from me, child?

00:26:33.727 --> 00:26:34.762 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-[laughs dismissively]

00:26:35.796 --> 00:26:38.199 position:19% line:83% align:start
So then, are these guys
here your new lackeys?

00:26:38.833 --> 00:26:41.068 position:16% line:83% align:start
You betrayed and got all
of my previous crew members

00:26:41.102 --> 00:26:42.770 position:24% line:89% align:start
killed on that day.

00:26:43.070 --> 00:26:44.672 position:24% line:89% align:start
Now give it to me.

00:26:44.939 --> 00:26:46.273 position:30% line:89% align:start
Give you what?

00:26:46.307 --> 00:26:48.709 position:24% line:83% align:start
The item you snuck
into the hole to steal.

00:26:49.343 --> 00:26:50.978 position:7% line:89% align:start
[scoffs] And who told you that?

00:26:51.011 --> 00:26:53.881 position:13% line:89% align:start
That would be me. [laughs]

00:26:53.914 --> 00:26:56.150 position:13% line:89% align:start
I went and found Boss Hai.

00:26:56.183 --> 00:26:58.652 position:38% line:83% align:start
[scoffs]
Who's this guy? Your new pet?

00:26:58.919 --> 00:26:59.987 position:38% line:83% align:start
[laughs]
[growls]

00:27:00.020 --> 00:27:01.388 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:27:01.422 --> 00:27:04.425 position:24% line:83% align:start
That boat had many
valuable items on it,

00:27:04.458 --> 00:27:06.894 position:27% line:83% align:start
but none as great
as what you stole.

00:27:07.828 --> 00:27:11.232 position:21% line:83% align:start
Hand it over, or else
we might have to take an arm

00:27:11.999 --> 00:27:13.434 position:38% line:89% align:start
or a leg.

00:27:13.467 --> 00:27:15.336 position:13% line:89% align:start
[thugs laughing menacingly]

00:27:16.303 --> 00:27:18.339 position:21% line:89% align:start
[monkey laughing] Hm?

00:27:19.707 --> 00:27:21.308 position:19% line:89% align:start
Huh? Oh, not you again.

00:27:21.342 --> 00:27:22.176 position:19% line:89% align:start
Why don't you get lost?

00:27:23.711 --> 00:27:25.312 position:24% line:89% align:start
[yawns] Excuse me.

00:27:25.346 --> 00:27:27.915 position:19% line:89% align:start
[tense harmonica music]

00:27:27.948 --> 00:27:30.885 position:16% line:83% align:start
You see, you have helpers
and I do too.

00:27:31.485 --> 00:27:33.454 position:27% line:83% align:start
[loud squeaking]
[groaning]

00:27:33.487 --> 00:27:35.122 position:30% line:83% align:start
-[upbeat music]
-Take this from me!

00:27:35.156 --> 00:27:36.257 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Now fight!
-Huh?

00:27:37.992 --> 00:27:39.093 position:30% line:89% align:start
Whoa, hang on.

00:27:39.126 --> 00:27:41.028 position:27% line:89% align:start
[thugs grunting]

00:27:41.061 --> 00:27:42.096 position:21% line:89% align:start
Wait a second, guys.

00:27:42.363 --> 00:27:44.265 position:27% line:83% align:start
Come on, it that
really the best you got?

00:27:44.298 --> 00:27:45.366 position:19% line:89% align:start
I don't even know him.

00:27:48.135 --> 00:27:49.170 position:30% line:89% align:start
Take them down!

00:27:52.473 --> 00:27:54.842 position:16% line:89% align:start
[upbeat music continues]

00:28:00.381 --> 00:28:02.016 position:27% line:89% align:start
[barrel shatters]

00:28:08.022 --> 00:28:09.757 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:28:13.460 --> 00:28:14.828 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[shouts]
-Hey--

00:28:19.233 --> 00:28:20.935 position:27% line:89% align:start
Thanks for that.

00:28:20.968 --> 00:28:22.436 position:24% line:83% align:start
When this is done,
I'll be sure to pay you back.

00:28:24.438 --> 00:28:26.740 position:38% line:83% align:start
Maybe so.
Wasn't that a little much?

00:28:26.774 --> 00:28:28.776 position:38% line:83% align:start
[scoffs]
Well, better them than me.

00:28:29.176 --> 00:28:31.245 position:27% line:83% align:start
If I were caught,
it'd've been worse than death.

00:28:33.013 --> 00:28:34.048 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:28:34.415 --> 00:28:37.284 position:27% line:89% align:start
[low tense music]

00:28:40.454 --> 00:28:42.022 position:33% line:89% align:start
What is this?

00:28:42.056 --> 00:28:44.458 position:19% line:83% align:start
And why did you hand it
off to a complete stranger?

00:28:45.059 --> 00:28:47.027 position:13% line:83% align:start
How else would they believe
we were working together?

00:28:47.529 --> 00:28:49.063 position:27% line:83% align:start
What if I wanted
it for myself?

00:28:49.096 --> 00:28:50.130 position:30% line:89% align:start
You'd be dead.

00:28:51.865 --> 00:28:53.367 position:27% line:89% align:start
Pretty big talk.

00:28:53.400 --> 00:28:54.435 position:21% line:89% align:start
Do you know who I am?

00:28:56.003 --> 00:28:58.239 position:19% line:83% align:start
No matter who you are,
I'll do what it takes.

00:29:04.378 --> 00:29:05.879 position:16% line:89% align:start
So the name's Yang Jian.

00:29:09.216 --> 00:29:10.251 position:35% line:89% align:start
Chenxiang?

00:29:11.586 --> 00:29:12.820 position:16% line:89% align:start
How do you know my name?

00:29:14.255 --> 00:29:15.356 position:24% line:89% align:start
Huh. So it's true.

00:29:17.057 --> 00:29:19.093 position:16% line:83% align:start
Someone went out of their
way to hire me to find you.

00:29:19.126 --> 00:29:20.794 position:27% line:89% align:start
[monkeys yelling]

00:29:21.563 --> 00:29:23.030 position:27% line:89% align:start
[water splashing]

00:29:25.099 --> 00:29:26.133 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:29:28.869 --> 00:29:30.371 position:27% line:89% align:start
[water bubbling]

00:29:33.140 --> 00:29:34.542 position:33% line:89% align:start
[whimpering]

00:29:34.576 --> 00:29:37.111 position:30% line:83% align:start
Yang Jian, what
are you doing here?

00:29:37.344 --> 00:29:38.812 position:7% line:89% align:start
I could ask the same question.

00:29:41.482 --> 00:29:42.850 position:38% line:89% align:start
Why, you.

00:29:43.851 --> 00:29:45.319 position:13% line:89% align:start
I just happened to be here.

00:29:45.352 --> 00:29:47.288 position:19% line:89% align:start
All of this, wasn't me.

00:29:49.890 --> 00:29:51.425 position:21% line:89% align:start
A knife to the back.

00:29:51.992 --> 00:29:53.060 position:19% line:89% align:start
Couldn't have been you.

00:29:53.093 --> 00:29:54.128 position:27% line:89% align:start
See. I told you.

00:29:55.429 --> 00:29:58.098 position:27% line:83% align:start
That guy who got
away is Chenxiang,

00:29:58.132 --> 00:29:59.400 position:19% line:89% align:start
the one you're seeking.

00:29:59.433 --> 00:30:01.935 position:13% line:89% align:start
Oh really? Wow, what luck.

00:30:01.969 --> 00:30:03.538 position:19% line:89% align:start
A common little thief.

00:30:03.571 --> 00:30:05.472 position:21% line:83% align:start
Is he worth that much
to the two of you?

00:30:06.508 --> 00:30:09.009 position:24% line:83% align:start
You really have no
idea who he is, do you?

00:30:09.443 --> 00:30:11.412 position:30% line:83% align:start
That boy, he's
from your school!

00:30:14.915 --> 00:30:17.885 position:21% line:83% align:start
Since you're already
involved in all this,

00:30:17.918 --> 00:30:20.921 position:24% line:83% align:start
to know the truth,
just go ask your Master.

00:30:20.954 --> 00:30:21.989 position:30% line:89% align:start
Master Yuding.

00:30:22.389 --> 00:30:24.526 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ominous music]

00:30:28.228 --> 00:30:30.497 position:30% line:5% align:start
[ship rushing]

00:30:53.621 --> 00:30:56.123 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:30:56.156 --> 00:30:58.560 position:30% line:89% align:start
[flute playing]

00:31:08.969 --> 00:31:11.573 position:24% line:89% align:start
[harmonica playing]

00:31:19.947 --> 00:31:21.348 position:19% line:89% align:start
Sir, that was amazing.

00:31:25.452 --> 00:31:28.556 position:10% line:83% align:start
Please tell your master that
Yang Jian is here to see him.

00:31:29.657 --> 00:31:30.491 position:30% line:89% align:start
Disciple Yang?

00:31:31.626 --> 00:31:33.160 position:21% line:89% align:start
Of course! Follow me!

00:31:35.697 --> 00:31:38.566 position:24% line:89% align:start
[soft guqin music]

00:32:13.535 --> 00:32:16.437 position:19% line:89% align:start
Yang Jian, you're here.

00:32:24.211 --> 00:32:25.580 position:27% line:89% align:start
How is your eye?

00:32:26.548 --> 00:32:28.516 position:19% line:89% align:start
Is it still closed off?

00:32:28.550 --> 00:32:29.584 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Jian] Yes.

00:32:31.385 --> 00:32:32.419 position:41% line:89% align:start
I see.

00:32:34.354 --> 00:32:36.290 position:33% line:83% align:start
I can open it
just a little bit,

00:32:36.624 --> 00:32:38.258 position:30% line:83% align:start
but when I do,
all I see is white.

00:32:39.493 --> 00:32:40.528 position:33% line:89% align:start
Nothing more.

00:32:44.331 --> 00:32:45.499 position:30% line:89% align:start
Hard to remedy.

00:32:46.568 --> 00:32:49.604 position:19% line:83% align:start
I suppose with a great
deal of strength,

00:32:49.637 --> 00:32:51.606 position:30% line:83% align:start
you could force
it open yourself,

00:32:52.640 --> 00:32:56.243 position:21% line:83% align:start
except it might make
the wound even worse.

00:32:56.276 --> 00:32:57.010 position:44% line:89% align:start
True.

00:32:57.612 --> 00:33:00.615 position:27% line:83% align:start
You were so young
when you arrived.

00:33:00.648 --> 00:33:02.983 position:27% line:83% align:start
I always thought
of you as a son.

00:33:05.787 --> 00:33:10.157 position:13% line:83% align:start
12 years ago, when you went
and sealed off Lotus Peak,

00:33:10.592 --> 00:33:13.661 position:7% line:89% align:start
and yet, the unrest carries on.

00:33:14.394 --> 00:33:18.265 position:24% line:83% align:start
The spiritual realm
grows weaker by the day.

00:33:18.298 --> 00:33:20.635 position:30% line:83% align:start
More demons and
monsters cropping up.

00:33:22.737 --> 00:33:27.675 position:7% line:83% align:start
I thought things would change,
but I was wrong in the end.

00:33:28.175 --> 00:33:32.647 position:27% line:83% align:start
Sooner or later,
catastrophe will return.

00:33:33.247 --> 00:33:36.584 position:21% line:83% align:start
Master, your teaching
has been "Do what one can."

00:33:37.417 --> 00:33:41.088 position:21% line:89% align:start
Yes. Do what you can.

00:33:41.556 --> 00:33:44.458 position:13% line:89% align:start
It is how to restore order,

00:33:45.259 --> 00:33:47.629 position:16% line:83% align:start
and only then the heavens
may begin to heal.

00:33:49.196 --> 00:33:50.030 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Jian] I understand.

00:33:56.604 --> 00:34:00.374 position:27% line:83% align:start
Master, recently
I happened to run into a boy.

00:34:00.407 --> 00:34:03.443 position:19% line:83% align:start
I was told he was your
disciple named Chenxiang.

00:34:03.477 --> 00:34:04.712 position:35% line:89% align:start
Chenxiang?!

00:34:05.847 --> 00:34:07.582 position:7% line:83% align:start
[scoffs in disgust] That's the
nephew you brought here!

00:34:07.782 --> 00:34:09.817 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[gasps]
-[Yuding] It's true.

00:34:10.450 --> 00:34:12.152 position:24% line:89% align:start
He's the same boy.

00:34:12.185 --> 00:34:13.521 position:30% line:89% align:start
[somber music]

00:34:13.555 --> 00:34:16.323 position:10% line:89% align:start
Not that he'd recognize you.

00:34:16.356 --> 00:34:19.561 position:19% line:83% align:start
He was only a baby when
you brought him here.

00:34:19.861 --> 00:34:22.095 position:21% line:83% align:start
And you haven't seen
each other since.

00:34:24.699 --> 00:34:27.569 position:27% line:83% align:start
I named him after
the agarwood tree,

00:34:28.468 --> 00:34:33.741 position:7% line:83% align:start
hoping he would grow steady and
serene, not brash or unkind.

00:34:34.441 --> 00:34:36.578 position:16% line:89% align:start
That was my intent.

00:34:37.645 --> 00:34:39.212 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:34:39.614 --> 00:34:43.350 position:19% line:83% align:start
To think that one of my
own students would murder

00:34:43.383 --> 00:34:44.619 position:33% line:89% align:start
his teacher.

00:34:47.655 --> 00:34:49.691 position:5% line:89% align:start
Go and take a look for yourself.

00:34:55.897 --> 00:34:59.366 position:10% line:83% align:start
The Master sealed his corpse
here, until we can bury him.

00:35:01.736 --> 00:35:03.403 position:24% line:83% align:start
Why would Chenxiang
kill an elder?

00:35:03.705 --> 00:35:05.540 position:10% line:89% align:start
[scoffs] I should have known.

00:35:05.573 --> 00:35:08.509 position:21% line:83% align:start
That child has always
been unruly and sinful.

00:35:09.209 --> 00:35:11.345 position:13% line:83% align:start
The Master's favor towards
you kept him from casting

00:35:11.378 --> 00:35:12.412 position:33% line:89% align:start
the boy out.

00:35:13.615 --> 00:35:15.449 position:16% line:83% align:start
Instead, he entrusted the
Second Elder with his training.

00:35:17.752 --> 00:35:18.886 position:7% line:89% align:start
Second Elder had a bad temper.

00:35:23.524 --> 00:35:24.859 position:27% line:89% align:start
What wounded him?

00:35:24.892 --> 00:35:26.393 position:13% line:89% align:start
[man] He didn't act alone.

00:35:26.894 --> 00:35:29.262 position:27% line:83% align:start
He allied himself
with Shen Gongbao.

00:35:29.296 --> 00:35:31.799 position:7% line:89% align:start
Shen Gongbao? Are you certain?

00:35:31.833 --> 00:35:33.400 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes.

00:35:33.668 --> 00:35:35.737 position:21% line:83% align:start
But I'm not sure how
he came in contact with him.

00:35:37.538 --> 00:35:40.240 position:16% line:83% align:start
He can multiply himself.
He's quite skilled at it.

00:35:40.808 --> 00:35:43.276 position:19% line:83% align:start
And they also stole an
artifact from Second Elder.

00:35:43.945 --> 00:35:46.246 position:30% line:83% align:start
-What artifact?
-It's the Lamp of Wishes.

00:35:46.581 --> 00:35:47.882 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

00:35:50.885 --> 00:35:53.855 position:24% line:5% align:start
[people chattering]

00:36:04.498 --> 00:36:06.834 position:30% line:89% align:start
[upbeat music]

00:36:10.705 --> 00:36:12.840 position:19% line:89% align:start
[indistinct chattering]

00:36:22.249 --> 00:36:23.851 position:24% line:89% align:start
Well done! [laughs]

00:36:23.885 --> 00:36:25.285 position:41% line:89% align:start
Bravo!

00:36:26.420 --> 00:36:27.789 position:35% line:89% align:start
Way to go!

00:36:29.557 --> 00:36:30.625 position:33% line:89% align:start
What's next?

00:36:32.927 --> 00:36:35.262 position:10% line:89% align:start
So far you have the lamp oil,

00:36:35.295 --> 00:36:37.397 position:13% line:83% align:start
which means the next thing
you got to get

00:36:37.431 --> 00:36:38.700 position:21% line:89% align:start
is it's precious lid.

00:36:39.634 --> 00:36:42.302 position:30% line:89% align:start
Oh, nice! Nice!

00:36:42.570 --> 00:36:43.604 position:24% line:89% align:start
I ran into someone.

00:36:44.739 --> 00:36:46.306 position:27% line:89% align:start
What's his name?

00:36:46.708 --> 00:36:48.876 position:27% line:83% align:start
Yang Jian. One of
my Master's students.

00:36:50.044 --> 00:36:51.445 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

00:36:51.478 --> 00:36:52.613 position:16% line:89% align:start
He was hired to find me.

00:36:53.681 --> 00:36:55.783 position:27% line:83% align:start
Do you think your
Master asked him to?

00:36:56.584 --> 00:36:58.318 position:24% line:83% align:start
I don't. He seemed
pretty unaware.

00:37:05.358 --> 00:37:05.993 position:44% line:89% align:start
Come.

00:37:15.469 --> 00:37:16.336 position:41% line:89% align:start
[huffs]

00:37:17.337 --> 00:37:18.673 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Shen] Keep up, kid.

00:37:19.774 --> 00:37:22.309 position:30% line:89% align:start
Come! [laughs]

00:37:24.377 --> 00:37:27.582 position:19% line:83% align:start
You only know Yang Jian
as an older disciple.

00:37:28.583 --> 00:37:31.418 position:19% line:83% align:start
But actually, that guy
is your uncle, you know.

00:37:32.787 --> 00:37:33.921 position:21% line:89% align:start
Is that really true?

00:37:34.956 --> 00:37:38.325 position:13% line:83% align:start
Your uncle is also the guy
who personally trapped

00:37:38.358 --> 00:37:39.761 position:10% line:89% align:start
your mother under Lotus Peak.

00:37:42.096 --> 00:37:45.298 position:19% line:83% align:start
Yang Jian is naturally
skilled at magic.

00:37:45.332 --> 00:37:47.902 position:13% line:83% align:start
He shattered the Lotus Lamp
into tiny pieces

00:37:47.935 --> 00:37:49.369 position:30% line:89% align:start
with his power.

00:37:50.037 --> 00:37:52.807 position:24% line:83% align:start
But if you can put
them all back together,

00:37:52.840 --> 00:37:55.042 position:16% line:89% align:start
it'll be as good as new.

00:37:55.076 --> 00:37:57.912 position:27% line:83% align:start
Once you do that,
you'll be able to use the lamp

00:37:57.945 --> 00:38:01.949 position:16% line:83% align:start
to crack open Lotus Peak
and save your mother.

00:38:09.524 --> 00:38:14.427 position:13% line:83% align:start
Yang Jian and your Master,
the whole lot of them

00:38:14.461 --> 00:38:16.363 position:30% line:83% align:start
are nothing but
a pack of wolves.

00:38:18.800 --> 00:38:20.835 position:16% line:89% align:start
Know what they did to me?

00:38:20.868 --> 00:38:22.970 position:13% line:89% align:start
At first it seemed not bad,

00:38:23.004 --> 00:38:26.073 position:33% line:83% align:start
they gave me
the title of general,

00:38:26.107 --> 00:38:28.743 position:19% line:83% align:start
just so they can let me
rot in the Eastern Sea.

00:38:31.478 --> 00:38:32.914 position:30% line:89% align:start
They talk big,

00:38:33.915 --> 00:38:36.584 position:5% line:89% align:start
but they're all just hypocrites!

00:38:36.918 --> 00:38:38.986 position:30% line:89% align:start
[tiger roaring]

00:38:41.388 --> 00:38:43.490 position:21% line:83% align:start
So I gritted my teeth
and bore it.

00:38:46.994 --> 00:38:51.732 position:7% line:83% align:start
And now after all these years,
I'll finally have my revenge!

00:38:52.834 --> 00:38:55.903 position:5% line:89% align:start
Once and for all, mark my words!

00:38:57.004 --> 00:38:58.840 position:35% line:89% align:start
[loud burp]

00:39:06.814 --> 00:39:07.882 position:38% line:89% align:start
My uncle.

00:39:07.915 --> 00:39:09.083 position:13% line:89% align:start
What does he want with me?

00:39:11.118 --> 00:39:13.087 position:19% line:83% align:start
He wants the Lotus Lamp
of course.

00:39:14.055 --> 00:39:18.125 position:7% line:83% align:start
It'll only activate if someone
of your mother's bloodline

00:39:18.159 --> 00:39:19.492 position:24% line:89% align:start
attempts to use it.

00:39:21.062 --> 00:39:22.930 position:38% line:89% align:start
Meaning?

00:39:29.136 --> 00:39:31.806 position:30% line:89% align:start
[serene music]

00:39:38.679 --> 00:39:40.948 position:19% line:83% align:start
And they also stole an
artifact from Second Elder.

00:39:41.515 --> 00:39:42.817 position:16% line:89% align:start
It's the Lamp of Wishes.

00:39:44.952 --> 00:39:47.688 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Wanluo] <i>He stole something</i>
 <i>from me. It was my sister's.</i>

00:39:48.055 --> 00:39:49.824 position:7% line:89% align:start
It's called the Lamp of Wishes.

00:39:50.691 --> 00:39:53.728 position:33% line:83% align:start
It's Wanluo.
I'll be waiting in Yingzhou.

00:39:54.929 --> 00:39:58.431 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:40:10.978 --> 00:40:13.547 position:19% line:5% align:start
[indistinct chattering]

00:40:19.520 --> 00:40:21.822 position:33% line:89% align:start
[soft music]

00:40:24.859 --> 00:40:27.995 position:24% line:89% align:start
[crowd applauding]

00:40:33.901 --> 00:40:34.936 position:21% line:89% align:start
[woman] It's started.

00:40:39.206 --> 00:40:41.108 position:24% line:89% align:start
[crowd chattering]

00:40:41.142 --> 00:40:43.611 position:27% line:83% align:start
[man] Incredible.
It's breathtaking.

00:40:49.050 --> 00:40:54.188 position:10% line:89% align:start
 Modest beauty, comfort me

00:40:54.956 --> 00:40:57.692 position:27% line:89% align:start
 How my heart

00:40:58.025 --> 00:41:00.728 position:24% line:89% align:start
 Longs for thee

00:41:00.928 --> 00:41:07.835 position:21% line:83% align:start
 Yet, no bridge can
cross the chasmed sea 

00:41:12.907 --> 00:41:15.810 position:27% line:89% align:start
 Here and now

00:41:15.843 --> 00:41:19.947 position:21% line:89% align:start
 I will give a vow

00:41:19.981 --> 00:41:24.251 position:27% line:89% align:start
 Made of jade

00:41:24.719 --> 00:41:27.088 position:33% line:89% align:start
 As a sign

00:41:27.655 --> 00:41:31.491 position:19% line:89% align:start
 For one so refined

00:41:31.926 --> 00:41:38.966 position:27% line:89% align:start
 Pure and true

00:41:42.336 --> 00:41:47.241 position:7% line:89% align:start
 Modest jewel she offers me

00:41:48.175 --> 00:41:53.814 position:10% line:89% align:start
 So I'll run far from thee

00:41:54.715 --> 00:42:01.122 position:21% line:83% align:start
 Yet I cannot cross
the chasmed sea 

00:42:04.792 --> 00:42:05.993 position:5% line:89% align:start
[man] Music without any players.

00:42:06.027 --> 00:42:07.194 position:24% line:89% align:start
How did they do it?

00:42:07.228 --> 00:42:10.931 position:24% line:89% align:start
[crowd applauding]

00:42:23.344 --> 00:42:24.645 position:24% line:89% align:start
[mystical whirring]

00:42:31.118 --> 00:42:33.788 position:33% line:89% align:start
[soft music]

00:42:42.063 --> 00:42:43.864 position:24% line:89% align:start
Attendant, my tea.

00:42:47.368 --> 00:42:48.569 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:42:48.969 --> 00:42:50.004 position:41% line:89% align:start
My tea.

00:42:50.237 --> 00:42:51.105 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Wanluo gasps]

00:43:01.115 --> 00:43:04.351 position:21% line:83% align:start
Sneaking in like that
gave me a fright.

00:43:06.754 --> 00:43:07.721 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Jian] Apologies.

00:43:08.089 --> 00:43:09.924 position:19% line:89% align:start
I was lost in thought.

00:43:09.957 --> 00:43:11.759 position:13% line:89% align:start
So distracted by your song.

00:43:12.126 --> 00:43:12.960 position:24% line:89% align:start
Please, forgive me.

00:43:13.694 --> 00:43:14.895 position:13% line:89% align:start
Should have said something.

00:43:19.200 --> 00:43:20.267 position:24% line:89% align:start
What did you like?

00:43:20.301 --> 00:43:21.135 position:30% line:89% align:start
I want to know.

00:43:22.236 --> 00:43:24.638 position:16% line:89% align:start
The song was so ethereal.

00:43:26.674 --> 00:43:29.143 position:30% line:83% align:start
It's Cao Zhi's
"Goddess of the Luo River."

00:43:29.176 --> 00:43:31.045 position:19% line:89% align:start
Pity it's so sorrowful.

00:43:36.383 --> 00:43:40.020 position:24% line:83% align:start
The lyrics speak of
pain and anguish.

00:43:41.021 --> 00:43:42.591 position:27% line:89% align:start
Quite a sad song.

00:43:47.194 --> 00:43:50.164 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:44:01.041 --> 00:44:01.876 position:30% line:89% align:start
Nothing to say?

00:44:04.278 --> 00:44:05.312 position:33% line:89% align:start
I'm not sure.

00:44:06.515 --> 00:44:09.183 position:5% line:83% align:start
When we spoke earlier, it almost
felt like we'd met before.

00:44:10.217 --> 00:44:12.086 position:7% line:89% align:start
Except I can't remember where.

00:44:14.255 --> 00:44:15.289 position:35% line:89% align:start
Who knows?

00:44:15.789 --> 00:44:17.391 position:16% line:89% align:start
Maybe it was in a dream.

00:44:20.461 --> 00:44:21.295 position:38% line:89% align:start
Hold on.

00:44:22.196 --> 00:44:23.230 position:44% line:89% align:start
Or...

00:44:24.965 --> 00:44:26.367 position:7% line:89% align:start
maybe it was more than a dream.

00:44:29.270 --> 00:44:30.304 position:35% line:89% align:start
Who knows?

00:44:33.841 --> 00:44:35.009 position:21% line:89% align:start
I ran into Chenxiang.

00:44:36.243 --> 00:44:37.278 position:38% line:89% align:start
You did?

00:44:39.280 --> 00:44:40.447 position:33% line:89% align:start
Where is he?

00:44:40.915 --> 00:44:42.449 position:33% line:89% align:start
He got away.

00:44:43.017 --> 00:44:45.986 position:13% line:83% align:start
I found out that Chenxiang
and I went to the same school.

00:44:46.820 --> 00:44:47.955 position:41% line:89% align:start
Really?

00:44:47.988 --> 00:44:49.089 position:24% line:89% align:start
Is that so, Erlang?

00:44:49.123 --> 00:44:50.291 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's Yang Jian.

00:44:50.824 --> 00:44:51.859 position:21% line:89% align:start
That's my real name.

00:44:52.126 --> 00:44:53.360 position:27% line:89% align:start
You're Yang Jian?

00:44:54.228 --> 00:44:55.996 position:10% line:89% align:start
That lamp you're looking for.

00:44:56.030 --> 00:44:57.932 position:30% line:83% align:start
It belonged to
Chenxiang's Master.

00:44:58.465 --> 00:45:01.302 position:19% line:83% align:start
What I want to know is
why you lied to me saying

00:45:01.335 --> 00:45:02.436 position:21% line:89% align:start
it was your sister's.

00:45:06.073 --> 00:45:10.811 position:19% line:83% align:start
Yang Jian, some things
are best left unknown.

00:45:11.345 --> 00:45:13.881 position:27% line:83% align:start
[magic whirring]
[groaning]

00:45:14.348 --> 00:45:16.150 position:19% line:89% align:start
Yang Jian, forgive me.

00:45:19.887 --> 00:45:21.021 position:33% line:89% align:start
[woman] Jian.

00:45:23.991 --> 00:45:24.825 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mother?

00:45:26.026 --> 00:45:27.228 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mother?

00:45:29.029 --> 00:45:29.863 position:44% line:89% align:start
Jian.

00:45:30.264 --> 00:45:31.265 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mother.

00:45:32.099 --> 00:45:33.100 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Mother!
-Jian.

00:45:34.468 --> 00:45:36.770 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Only you...
-Don't go!

00:45:36.804 --> 00:45:37.905 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Mother]
...can split the mountain.

00:45:37.938 --> 00:45:39.406 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mother!

00:45:52.987 --> 00:45:54.054 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mother.

00:46:17.344 --> 00:46:20.247 position:30% line:89% align:start
[serene music]

00:46:52.580 --> 00:46:55.349 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:47:28.982 --> 00:47:30.518 position:41% line:83% align:start
[gasps]
[wood cracking]

00:47:31.985 --> 00:47:34.488 position:5% line:89% align:start
Woo! Pretty good defensive move.

00:47:34.522 --> 00:47:35.989 position:19% line:89% align:start
But a bit over the top.

00:47:41.061 --> 00:47:42.096 position:38% line:89% align:start
Hold on.

00:47:44.098 --> 00:47:45.099 position:16% line:89% align:start
You want the Lotus Lamp?

00:47:46.701 --> 00:47:47.901 position:27% line:89% align:start
Why do you care?

00:47:50.638 --> 00:47:52.439 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm guessing you know,
I'm your uncle.

00:47:54.609 --> 00:47:57.044 position:10% line:83% align:start
That's right. I'm the one who
brought you to Jin Xia Cave.

00:47:57.612 --> 00:47:58.946 position:16% line:89% align:start
You were just a baby.

00:47:59.446 --> 00:48:00.548 position:13% line:89% align:start
You didn't have a name yet.

00:48:01.315 --> 00:48:04.184 position:27% line:89% align:start
You were so tiny.

00:48:06.086 --> 00:48:09.022 position:16% line:83% align:start
The Second Elder, I knew
he had a bad temper.

00:48:10.625 --> 00:48:12.393 position:13% line:83% align:start
I don't know why the Master
put you in his care.

00:48:14.128 --> 00:48:15.329 position:24% line:83% align:start
Was it really hard
for you there?

00:48:17.164 --> 00:48:18.432 position:33% line:89% align:start
It was swell.

00:48:18.700 --> 00:48:20.134 position:16% line:89% align:start
I wasn't taught a thing.

00:48:20.167 --> 00:48:22.504 position:21% line:83% align:start
Just beaten to a pulp
and starved.

00:48:23.137 --> 00:48:24.639 position:7% line:89% align:start
Called me a worthless bastard.

00:48:29.143 --> 00:48:30.244 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry.

00:48:30.277 --> 00:48:31.345 position:30% line:89% align:start
I had no idea.

00:48:34.181 --> 00:48:36.450 position:16% line:83% align:start
Even if that's the case,
you shouldn't have killed him.

00:48:36.483 --> 00:48:39.286 position:10% line:83% align:start
And you shouldn't have buried
my mother under Lotus Peak!

00:48:39.319 --> 00:48:42.189 position:24% line:89% align:start
[magical whooshing]

00:48:42.757 --> 00:48:43.991 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:48:44.024 --> 00:48:44.659 position:35% line:89% align:start
Let me go!

00:48:46.126 --> 00:48:47.161 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Lihong laughing]

00:48:47.394 --> 00:48:49.129 position:21% line:89% align:start
Yang Jian, well done!

00:48:49.163 --> 00:48:50.964 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ship whirring]

00:48:50.998 --> 00:48:53.635 position:7% line:83% align:start
Chenxiang, you're under arrest
for murdering your teacher.

00:48:55.670 --> 00:48:57.137 position:5% line:83% align:start
-We have orders to bring you in.
-You--

00:48:57.505 --> 00:48:59.039 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Lihong] Turn yourself in!

00:49:07.181 --> 00:49:10.217 position:33% line:89% align:start
[explosions]

00:49:26.467 --> 00:49:28.703 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

00:49:29.704 --> 00:49:32.607 position:35% line:83% align:start
Yang Jian!
This time we saw you do it!

00:49:32.640 --> 00:49:33.474 position:24% line:89% align:start
You let him escape!

00:49:35.175 --> 00:49:38.378 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm afraid we have to
place you under arrest.

00:49:38.412 --> 00:49:39.714 position:33% line:89% align:start
Don't bother.

00:49:39.747 --> 00:49:41.381 position:24% line:83% align:start
Once I take care of
things with the kid,

00:49:41.415 --> 00:49:44.151 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'll turn myself in,
so don't worry, 'kay?

00:49:45.052 --> 00:49:47.689 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Lihong grunts]
[lute strums]

00:49:47.722 --> 00:49:49.289 position:27% line:89% align:start
[wood shattering]

00:49:51.458 --> 00:49:52.493 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:49:53.360 --> 00:49:55.630 position:27% line:89% align:start
[lute strumming]

00:49:58.232 --> 00:50:00.501 position:24% line:89% align:start
[harmonica playing]

00:50:07.341 --> 00:50:09.677 position:10% line:89% align:start
Yang Jian, you brought this.

00:50:10.745 --> 00:50:12.580 position:30% line:83% align:start
[bells ringing]
[grunts]

00:50:12.614 --> 00:50:15.415 position:24% line:89% align:start
[magical whooshing]

00:50:15.449 --> 00:50:18.285 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

00:50:20.487 --> 00:50:23.457 position:30% line:89% align:start
[wind blowing]

00:50:29.564 --> 00:50:31.198 position:19% line:89% align:start
Release the fiery wind!

00:50:31.231 --> 00:50:33.233 position:30% line:83% align:start
[lute playing]
[grunts]

00:50:35.202 --> 00:50:36.571 position:27% line:89% align:start
[loud explosion]

00:50:38.171 --> 00:50:41.074 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:50:51.886 --> 00:50:56.056 position:27% line:83% align:start
[floor shatters]
[creature growls]

00:50:56.791 --> 00:50:59.459 position:24% line:83% align:start
- Heavenly strings!
- [lute strums]

00:51:06.701 --> 00:51:08.068 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ferret squeaks]

00:51:08.903 --> 00:51:10.705 position:10% line:89% align:start
Brother number four is here.

00:51:10.738 --> 00:51:12.272 position:44% line:89% align:start
Wow.

00:51:12.306 --> 00:51:13.608 position:19% line:89% align:start
That's not really fair.

00:51:13.641 --> 00:51:14.642 position:7% line:89% align:start
Doesn't really fit your style.

00:51:16.778 --> 00:51:19.814 position:21% line:83% align:start
If I'm not mistaken,
the last time you fought

00:51:19.847 --> 00:51:23.483 position:24% line:83% align:start
the four of us, you
yourself didn't exactly play

00:51:23.518 --> 00:51:24.852 position:21% line:89% align:start
by the rules either.

00:51:25.520 --> 00:51:27.722 position:21% line:89% align:start
Good point. [yelping]

00:51:28.790 --> 00:51:30.123 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Lihai] Yang Jian.

00:51:30.490 --> 00:51:31.793 position:19% line:89% align:start
I was vouching for you.

00:51:31.826 --> 00:51:34.127 position:27% line:83% align:start
Said you weren't
involved in any of this.

00:51:34.161 --> 00:51:34.796 position:41% line:89% align:start
But...

00:51:37.464 --> 00:51:39.399 position:10% line:89% align:start
it's clear that I was wrong.

00:51:39.433 --> 00:51:41.234 position:5% line:89% align:start
If you admit what you have done,

00:51:41.268 --> 00:51:43.705 position:16% line:83% align:start
I promise to support you
at the Celestial Court.

00:51:43.738 --> 00:51:46.106 position:44% line:83% align:start
Huh?
What exactly did I do?

00:51:46.306 --> 00:51:47.709 position:27% line:89% align:start
Don't play dumb.

00:51:47.742 --> 00:51:50.645 position:13% line:83% align:start
It's clear to us both that
you and Chenxiang killed

00:51:50.678 --> 00:51:51.713 position:27% line:89% align:start
the Second Elder.

00:51:52.647 --> 00:51:54.448 position:44% line:83% align:start
Wait.
[loud dong]

00:51:57.619 --> 00:51:59.754 position:27% line:83% align:start
-[loud clanging]
-Ow!

00:51:59.787 --> 00:52:02.189 position:35% line:89% align:start
[muttering]

00:52:02.557 --> 00:52:05.560 position:13% line:83% align:start
Hey, new guy! Do you really
have to make that much noise?

00:52:05.593 --> 00:52:06.894 position:24% line:83% align:start
Have you never been
in jail before?

00:52:08.362 --> 00:52:09.797 position:30% line:89% align:start
Huh? Yang Jian?

00:52:11.431 --> 00:52:12.634 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yo, yo, yo!

00:52:12.900 --> 00:52:14.535 position:19% line:89% align:start
Long time, no see, man.

00:52:14.802 --> 00:52:16.470 position:30% line:89% align:start
[bright music]

00:52:16.504 --> 00:52:17.538 position:33% line:89% align:start
And you are?

00:52:17.772 --> 00:52:19.574 position:33% line:89% align:start
[scoffs] Wha?

00:52:21.676 --> 00:52:23.778 position:16% line:83% align:start
Why, I'm the--the--the--
the--the--

00:52:23.811 --> 00:52:25.813 position:35% line:83% align:start
big guard,
the elixir, the tall guy.

00:52:25.847 --> 00:52:28.181 position:24% line:83% align:start
The super tall guy,
and then bang!

00:52:28.215 --> 00:52:30.350 position:10% line:83% align:start
[yelling] And then we went--
[imitating ships]

00:52:30.384 --> 00:52:32.720 position:24% line:83% align:start
And then we went--
[imitating ships]

00:52:37.525 --> 00:52:39.761 position:30% line:89% align:start
[sighs, groans]

00:52:40.360 --> 00:52:41.596 position:41% line:89% align:start
20,000.

00:52:42.262 --> 00:52:42.897 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh.

00:52:44.364 --> 00:52:47.167 position:24% line:89% align:start
[creatures roaring]

00:52:49.871 --> 00:52:52.974 position:10% line:89% align:start
Hey, you might be Yang Jian,

00:52:53.007 --> 00:52:55.877 position:30% line:83% align:start
but in my eyes,
you're nothing at all.

00:52:55.910 --> 00:52:58.713 position:19% line:83% align:start
You show me respect or
I'll beat it into you.

00:53:00.715 --> 00:53:02.449 position:10% line:89% align:start
Thank you, sir. Take it easy.

00:53:02.984 --> 00:53:04.552 position:30% line:83% align:start
-That's right.
-[guard] You better cut

00:53:04.585 --> 00:53:06.186 position:21% line:89% align:start
the noise! Right now!

00:53:06.486 --> 00:53:07.689 position:27% line:89% align:start
[prisoner yowls]

00:53:10.992 --> 00:53:13.995 position:21% line:83% align:start
Hey, Yang Jian, even
though you're the reason

00:53:14.028 --> 00:53:15.997 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm in this prison
to begin with,

00:53:16.030 --> 00:53:18.533 position:21% line:83% align:start
I don't hold a grudge
about those kind of things.

00:53:18.566 --> 00:53:19.834 position:21% line:89% align:start
What's done is done.

00:53:25.673 --> 00:53:28.576 position:38% line:83% align:start
Come on!
[yelping]

00:53:28.609 --> 00:53:30.343 position:19% line:83% align:start
If you, you don't watch
out for the guards in here,

00:53:30.377 --> 00:53:31.779 position:27% line:83% align:start
they'll beat you
to a pulp, okay?

00:53:32.980 --> 00:53:35.016 position:7% line:89% align:start
[sighs] Are you even listening?

00:53:35.049 --> 00:53:35.917 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hey!

00:53:38.318 --> 00:53:40.688 position:24% line:89% align:start
[creature snoring]

00:53:40.722 --> 00:53:42.523 position:24% line:89% align:start
[thunder rumbling]

00:53:48.529 --> 00:53:50.998 position:24% line:89% align:start
[thunder rumbling]

00:53:51.632 --> 00:53:53.768 position:35% line:89% align:start
[growling]

00:53:56.571 --> 00:53:59.040 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yelping]

00:53:59.073 --> 00:54:00.975 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gong ringing]

00:54:01.008 --> 00:54:02.610 position:27% line:89% align:start
[cannon banging]

00:54:02.643 --> 00:54:03.945 position:27% line:89% align:start
[loud explosion]

00:54:04.545 --> 00:54:05.880 position:24% line:89% align:start
[creature roaring]

00:54:08.850 --> 00:54:11.853 position:24% line:89% align:start
[lightning zapping]

00:54:16.691 --> 00:54:18.291 position:27% line:89% align:start
[loud explosion]

00:54:20.360 --> 00:54:22.830 position:33% line:83% align:start
Ooh! [laughs]
Sounds like a fight.

00:54:22.864 --> 00:54:24.766 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh yeah!

00:54:24.799 --> 00:54:25.867 position:19% line:89% align:start
This ought to be good.

00:54:25.900 --> 00:54:28.401 position:10% line:89% align:start
Maybe it's a breakout, right?

00:54:29.469 --> 00:54:30.303 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yang Jian.

00:54:30.972 --> 00:54:31.806 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hey.

00:54:33.775 --> 00:54:36.476 position:16% line:83% align:start
Are you trying to tell me
they're here for you?

00:54:37.745 --> 00:54:38.880 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-[gasps]

00:54:40.848 --> 00:54:42.315 position:21% line:89% align:start
All of you get back!

00:54:42.349 --> 00:54:44.519 position:21% line:83% align:start
You better watch it!
You hear me?

00:54:44.852 --> 00:54:45.887 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hey.

00:54:50.525 --> 00:54:51.926 position:30% line:89% align:start
[guard grunts]

00:54:55.863 --> 00:54:57.297 position:27% line:89% align:start
Well, you coming?

00:54:59.867 --> 00:55:00.902 position:44% line:89% align:start
Okay.

00:55:00.935 --> 00:55:03.671 position:30% line:89% align:start
[upbeat music]

00:55:04.872 --> 00:55:06.707 position:41% line:83% align:start
[guard]
Hey! Back in your cells!

00:55:13.014 --> 00:55:15.315 position:21% line:89% align:start
[prisoners grunting]

00:55:18.519 --> 00:55:19.987 position:30% line:89% align:start
So the elixir,

00:55:20.021 --> 00:55:20.855 position:24% line:89% align:start
what was it really?

00:55:21.989 --> 00:55:23.691 position:19% line:89% align:start
Does it really matter?

00:55:24.091 --> 00:55:25.960 position:24% line:83% align:start
Let's just focus on
getting out of here.

00:55:25.993 --> 00:55:27.061 position:27% line:83% align:start
[wall shattering]
[both shout]

00:55:29.564 --> 00:55:30.798 position:19% line:89% align:start
Xiaotian, where is he?

00:55:31.933 --> 00:55:32.967 position:35% line:89% align:start
Over there!

00:55:33.500 --> 00:55:35.468 position:33% line:89% align:start
[funky music]

00:55:35.937 --> 00:55:37.538 position:16% line:89% align:start
Uh, we better get moving.

00:55:38.172 --> 00:55:39.607 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:55:51.451 --> 00:55:53.754 position:33% line:89% align:start
[boy yelling]

00:55:57.925 --> 00:55:59.727 position:27% line:89% align:start
Help me out! Hey!

00:55:59.760 --> 00:56:00.795 position:38% line:89% align:start
Help me!

00:56:06.868 --> 00:56:08.903 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

00:56:16.644 --> 00:56:17.979 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[Xiaotian cheers]
-[man] Erlang!

00:56:21.682 --> 00:56:22.817 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yang Jian!

00:56:25.653 --> 00:56:27.688 position:35% line:89% align:start
[shouting]

00:56:27.722 --> 00:56:29.056 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:56:29.090 --> 00:56:30.157 position:30% line:83% align:start
It's either one
thing or another.

00:56:31.158 --> 00:56:32.526 position:24% line:83% align:start
First we're aimless
bounty hunters,

00:56:34.962 --> 00:56:35.997 position:7% line:89% align:start
and then fugitives in Penglai.

00:56:42.904 --> 00:56:44.705 position:35% line:89% align:start
[shouting]

00:56:44.972 --> 00:56:47.041 position:10% line:89% align:start
Comrades, you've been loyal.

00:56:47.074 --> 00:56:48.509 position:13% line:89% align:start
And you've suffered for it.

00:56:48.542 --> 00:56:49.944 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:56:49.977 --> 00:56:51.012 position:33% line:83% align:start
Wouldn't have
it any other way!

00:56:51.245 --> 00:56:52.780 position:35% line:89% align:start
Our choice.

00:56:52.813 --> 00:56:55.616 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Xiaotian cheering]

00:57:02.023 --> 00:57:03.724 position:30% line:89% align:start
[fire rumbling]

00:57:04.091 --> 00:57:04.926 position:38% line:89% align:start
Xiaotian.

00:57:11.933 --> 00:57:14.835 position:27% line:89% align:start
[sharp whirring]

00:57:20.007 --> 00:57:21.474 position:30% line:89% align:start
[engine booms]

00:57:27.915 --> 00:57:30.084 position:33% line:89% align:start
[boy yelling]

00:57:33.521 --> 00:57:35.056 position:33% line:83% align:start
Erlang, where
are we going now?

00:57:48.002 --> 00:57:50.037 position:21% line:5% align:start
The lamp's last piece
is in that pagoda.

00:57:53.574 --> 00:57:55.910 position:16% line:83% align:start
The light they're using,
it comes from the lid

00:57:55.943 --> 00:57:57.578 position:33% line:89% align:start
of the lamp.

00:57:57.611 --> 00:58:00.681 position:21% line:83% align:start
Yeah, I have no idea
how they got it though.

00:58:00.715 --> 00:58:03.050 position:21% line:83% align:start
Nowadays they use it
to guide flying ships.

00:58:05.619 --> 00:58:06.754 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:58:07.154 --> 00:58:08.589 position:19% line:89% align:start
Must you drink so much?

00:58:08.823 --> 00:58:09.790 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Shen laughs]

00:58:10.858 --> 00:58:15.296 position:16% line:83% align:start
Whether heaven or hearse,
in a flash, it all goes,

00:58:15.329 --> 00:58:17.798 position:24% line:89% align:start
so drink your fill.

00:58:17.832 --> 00:58:21.602 position:10% line:89% align:start
That's all one needs to know.

00:58:22.069 --> 00:58:24.171 position:21% line:89% align:start
[lighthouse creaking]

00:58:35.816 --> 00:58:38.853 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

00:58:43.958 --> 00:58:44.992 position:38% line:89% align:start
That you?

00:58:45.026 --> 00:58:47.762 position:19% line:89% align:start
If it isn't Mo Liqing!

00:58:47.795 --> 00:58:50.331 position:19% line:83% align:start
Oh-ho! Been a real long
time, my old friend!

00:58:50.364 --> 00:58:52.166 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:58:52.867 --> 00:58:54.168 position:16% line:89% align:start
I've been waiting.

00:58:55.870 --> 00:58:58.005 position:33% line:89% align:start
At long last.

00:58:58.372 --> 00:59:02.143 position:13% line:83% align:start
And you must be Chenxiang,
murderer and fugitive.

00:59:02.176 --> 00:59:05.012 position:13% line:89% align:start
Oh, that's enough of that.

00:59:05.279 --> 00:59:06.647 position:38% line:89% align:start
[shouts]

00:59:07.715 --> 00:59:11.252 position:16% line:83% align:start
You should already know,
the Phoenixes you trapped,

00:59:11.285 --> 00:59:13.020 position:13% line:89% align:start
they'll break free one day.

00:59:15.022 --> 00:59:19.060 position:16% line:83% align:start
My brothers and I have no
desire to see that day arrive.

00:59:19.093 --> 00:59:20.694 position:19% line:89% align:start
It shall summon chaos.

00:59:21.362 --> 00:59:23.798 position:21% line:89% align:start
But it's inevitable.

00:59:23.831 --> 00:59:26.300 position:13% line:83% align:start
You think you can suppress
the Phoenixes forever?

00:59:28.102 --> 00:59:31.138 position:19% line:83% align:start
Mount Hua still stands
despite its appearance

00:59:31.172 --> 00:59:33.240 position:16% line:89% align:start
and what you may believe.

00:59:33.274 --> 00:59:37.011 position:19% line:83% align:start
We risked everything to
restrain those birds' powers.

00:59:37.978 --> 00:59:41.348 position:10% line:83% align:start
If I can hold it another day,
that's one more day it stands.

00:59:42.683 --> 00:59:44.685 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Shen laughs]

00:59:44.718 --> 00:59:48.089 position:24% line:83% align:start
Mo Liqing, friend,
this go 'round,

00:59:48.122 --> 00:59:50.958 position:27% line:83% align:start
you're my enemy,
and no longer a friend.

00:59:52.726 --> 00:59:54.161 position:30% line:89% align:start
[driving music]

00:59:58.199 --> 00:59:59.600 position:30% line:89% align:start
[swords clang]

00:59:59.934 --> 01:00:01.602 position:38% line:89% align:start
[burps]

01:00:09.376 --> 01:00:11.879 position:30% line:83% align:start
[swords clang]
[Shen grunts]

01:00:21.155 --> 01:00:23.757 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tiger roars]

01:00:33.968 --> 01:00:35.102 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

01:00:37.938 --> 01:00:40.641 position:30% line:89% align:start
[driving music]

01:00:59.293 --> 01:01:01.762 position:27% line:83% align:start
[wood shattering]
[shouting]

01:01:10.204 --> 01:01:11.238 position:35% line:89% align:start
[shouting]

01:01:13.073 --> 01:01:16.076 position:30% line:89% align:start
[deep rumbling]

01:01:19.947 --> 01:01:22.883 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

01:01:28.822 --> 01:01:31.091 position:27% line:89% align:start
[sword thunders]

01:01:36.263 --> 01:01:39.099 position:24% line:83% align:start
Oh. Guess we're not
holding back then.

01:01:39.133 --> 01:01:42.002 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

01:01:44.138 --> 01:01:46.941 position:30% line:89% align:start
[tiger roaring]

01:01:57.418 --> 01:01:59.820 position:27% line:83% align:start
[music continues]
[tigers roaring]

01:02:13.400 --> 01:02:15.236 position:27% line:89% align:start
[swords clanging]

01:02:16.370 --> 01:02:18.772 position:19% line:89% align:start
Your Duplication trick?

01:02:18.806 --> 01:02:21.475 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Liqing grunting]
[music continues]

01:02:32.953 --> 01:02:33.921 position:33% line:89% align:start
[loud belch]

01:02:37.825 --> 01:02:40.194 position:30% line:89% align:start
[both thudding]

01:02:48.035 --> 01:02:49.370 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Chenxiang yells]

01:02:53.140 --> 01:02:54.475 position:19% line:89% align:start
You can duplicate too?

01:02:55.309 --> 01:02:57.011 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

01:03:00.247 --> 01:03:01.782 position:33% line:89% align:start
[sword thuds]

01:03:08.889 --> 01:03:11.825 position:7% line:89% align:start
To have mastered duplication...

01:03:11.859 --> 01:03:16.196 position:13% line:83% align:start
I see that Shen Gongbao has
taught you his dark magic.

01:03:17.197 --> 01:03:19.199 position:16% line:89% align:start
To win, I'll do anything.

01:03:28.142 --> 01:03:30.344 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

01:03:36.250 --> 01:03:38.852 position:30% line:89% align:start
[tiger growls]

01:03:55.369 --> 01:03:57.471 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Shen gasps]
Chenxiang! Run now!

01:03:59.473 --> 01:04:01.609 position:27% line:89% align:start
[swords thudding]

01:04:06.146 --> 01:04:08.516 position:30% line:89% align:start
[loud crashing]

01:04:09.651 --> 01:04:11.318 position:30% line:89% align:start
[both shouting]

01:04:13.087 --> 01:04:13.921 position:35% line:89% align:start
Chenxiang!

01:04:15.055 --> 01:04:16.524 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

01:04:26.400 --> 01:04:29.269 position:27% line:89% align:start
[loud explosion]

01:04:34.241 --> 01:04:37.077 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Chenxiang panting]

01:04:40.214 --> 01:04:43.050 position:30% line:89% align:start
[somber music]

01:04:43.250 --> 01:04:46.086 position:30% line:89% align:start
[both groaning]

01:04:50.190 --> 01:04:53.127 position:24% line:89% align:start
[swords swooshing]

01:04:56.296 --> 01:04:57.665 position:30% line:89% align:start
[tiger growls]

01:05:11.445 --> 01:05:14.348 position:24% line:89% align:start
[swords thundering]

01:05:15.249 --> 01:05:16.518 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Shen] Get going!

01:05:16.551 --> 01:05:19.019 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

01:05:23.357 --> 01:05:24.491 position:24% line:89% align:start
[swords clattering]

01:05:30.097 --> 01:05:31.231 position:41% line:89% align:start
Go now!

01:05:48.282 --> 01:05:49.483 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Shen groaning]

01:06:07.401 --> 01:06:09.704 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Shen coughing]

01:06:10.672 --> 01:06:11.706 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hello.

01:06:12.473 --> 01:06:14.576 position:16% line:89% align:start
Looks like we meet again.

01:06:15.242 --> 01:06:17.444 position:30% line:83% align:start
Need to make an
entrance, don't you? Ha!

01:06:17.478 --> 01:06:18.613 position:24% line:89% align:start
[swords whooshing]

01:06:22.517 --> 01:06:25.118 position:33% line:89% align:start
[sword booms]

01:06:36.497 --> 01:06:39.399 position:24% line:89% align:start
[melancholy music]

01:06:45.339 --> 01:06:46.708 position:30% line:89% align:start
[tiger groans]

01:06:54.749 --> 01:06:56.250 position:30% line:89% align:start
[tiger groans]

01:07:00.153 --> 01:07:02.624 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tiger roars]

01:07:03.490 --> 01:07:06.360 position:24% line:89% align:start
[magical whirring]

01:07:09.564 --> 01:07:11.633 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:07:18.338 --> 01:07:19.574 position:35% line:89% align:start
[thudding]

01:07:50.805 --> 01:07:52.272 position:33% line:89% align:start
Shen Gongbao.

01:07:52.306 --> 01:07:53.708 position:24% line:89% align:start
[melancholic music]

01:07:54.876 --> 01:07:56.644 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yang Jian.

01:07:57.645 --> 01:07:58.680 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's good to see you.

01:08:00.280 --> 01:08:02.449 position:7% line:89% align:start
I heard you fell on hard times.

01:08:03.718 --> 01:08:05.653 position:13% line:89% align:start
Your Third Eye went blind.

01:08:07.822 --> 01:08:12.760 position:10% line:83% align:start
I feel for that boy who split
Mount Tao all those years ago.

01:08:14.328 --> 01:08:17.532 position:21% line:83% align:start
I was always fond of
that young Yang Jian.

01:08:18.933 --> 01:08:21.201 position:33% line:83% align:start
Shen Gongbao,
where's Chenxiang?

01:08:24.772 --> 01:08:26.708 position:21% line:89% align:start
He ran off somewhere.

01:08:30.243 --> 01:08:33.881 position:21% line:83% align:start
That Chenxiang is one
heartless, ruthless kid.

01:08:33.915 --> 01:08:36.517 position:24% line:83% align:start
I was the same way
when I was that age.

01:08:36.918 --> 01:08:38.553 position:38% line:89% align:start
[coughs]

01:08:38.953 --> 01:08:41.121 position:24% line:83% align:start
I guess that means
he's my successor.

01:08:44.391 --> 01:08:45.760 position:30% line:83% align:start
Do you have any
idea where he'd go?

01:08:46.894 --> 01:08:49.129 position:35% line:83% align:start
That little
secret place of his.

01:08:53.433 --> 01:08:54.468 position:38% line:89% align:start
Mount Li.

01:08:55.737 --> 01:08:57.572 position:27% line:89% align:start
Cross-Moon Pool.

01:08:57.605 --> 01:08:58.840 position:35% line:89% align:start
[coughing]

01:08:59.941 --> 01:09:02.810 position:27% line:89% align:start
[tiger growling]

01:09:15.455 --> 01:09:16.490 position:33% line:89% align:start
Your wounds.

01:09:16.524 --> 01:09:17.625 position:33% line:89% align:start
Who did this?

01:09:19.694 --> 01:09:22.396 position:24% line:89% align:start
Life is too short.

01:09:23.898 --> 01:09:27.367 position:7% line:89% align:start
Full of sorrow, til we're gone.

01:09:28.903 --> 01:09:31.673 position:21% line:89% align:start
Yet though I leave...

01:09:33.775 --> 01:09:34.809 position:44% line:89% align:start
time,

01:09:36.276 --> 01:09:39.246 position:27% line:89% align:start
it will flow on.

01:10:11.579 --> 01:10:13.548 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Xiaotian laughs]

01:10:13.781 --> 01:10:14.949 position:19% line:89% align:start
Can we trust this guy?

01:10:16.784 --> 01:10:19.921 position:16% line:89% align:start
[laughs] All right, guys!

01:10:19.954 --> 01:10:22.456 position:5% line:89% align:start
Everything's been taken care of!

01:10:22.489 --> 01:10:23.524 position:35% line:89% align:start
Very safe.

01:10:23.725 --> 01:10:25.593 position:19% line:89% align:start
[yelping] Hey, hold on.

01:10:25.626 --> 01:10:26.761 position:16% line:89% align:start
There isn't room for you.

01:10:26.794 --> 01:10:28.261 position:24% line:89% align:start
It only seats one.

01:10:28.563 --> 01:10:29.931 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Xiaotian groans]

01:10:30.497 --> 01:10:32.867 position:30% line:89% align:start
[bright music]

01:10:33.067 --> 01:10:33.901 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

01:10:38.706 --> 01:10:40.641 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

01:10:44.545 --> 01:10:46.547 position:21% line:89% align:start
[groans] Cheapskate!

01:10:46.581 --> 01:10:48.315 position:19% line:89% align:start
What? You! You little!

01:10:54.555 --> 01:10:56.891 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

01:11:10.605 --> 01:11:12.707 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ramp rumbling]

01:11:17.812 --> 01:11:19.013 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Xiaotian] I want to go too!

01:11:19.479 --> 01:11:20.748 position:24% line:89% align:start
No! You won't fit!

01:11:21.348 --> 01:11:23.951 position:30% line:83% align:start
Hang on a sec!
I forgot to tell you!

01:11:23.985 --> 01:11:25.653 position:19% line:83% align:start
When going through the
hole you can get nauseous!

01:11:25.686 --> 01:11:27.387 position:21% line:89% align:start
Huh? What'd you say?

01:11:28.055 --> 01:11:28.890 position:38% line:89% align:start
Hang on!

01:11:30.525 --> 01:11:31.926 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whooshing]

01:11:32.994 --> 01:11:37.665 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Jian yelling]
[jazzy music]

01:11:49.944 --> 01:11:51.946 position:33% line:89% align:start
[ice cracks]

01:11:55.482 --> 01:11:56.818 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ship crashes]

01:11:58.953 --> 01:12:02.890 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

01:12:03.456 --> 01:12:07.862 position:24% line:83% align:start
[overlapping voices
speaking indistinctly]

01:12:10.932 --> 01:12:11.966 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Jian vomits]

01:12:21.676 --> 01:12:22.910 position:27% line:89% align:start
This is Chang'an?

01:12:38.092 --> 01:12:41.963 position:27% line:83% align:start
[wind whistling]
[crows cawing]

01:12:47.134 --> 01:12:48.903 position:13% line:89% align:start
The Mortal Realm is at war.

01:13:00.748 --> 01:13:03.784 position:33% line:5% align:start
[soft music]

01:13:33.814 --> 01:13:35.016 position:33% line:89% align:start
You made it.

01:13:42.957 --> 01:13:43.991 position:35% line:89% align:start
A new lamp,

01:13:44.992 --> 01:13:46.027 position:38% line:89% align:start
lamp oil,

01:13:47.128 --> 01:13:48.696 position:27% line:89% align:start
the old lamp lid.

01:13:49.597 --> 01:13:50.865 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's now complete.

01:13:50.898 --> 01:13:53.200 position:30% line:89% align:start
[lamp whirring]

01:13:55.703 --> 01:13:58.072 position:27% line:89% align:start
[mystical music]

01:14:03.878 --> 01:14:05.046 position:33% line:89% align:start
What is this?

01:14:08.249 --> 01:14:10.918 position:7% line:89% align:start
Yang Jian, I know you're here.

01:14:11.252 --> 01:14:12.620 position:35% line:89% align:start
Don't hide.

01:14:12.954 --> 01:14:15.022 position:24% line:83% align:start
Why don't you tell
Chenxiang the true purpose

01:14:15.056 --> 01:14:16.489 position:24% line:89% align:start
of the Lotus Lamp?

01:14:18.893 --> 01:14:19.927 position:27% line:89% align:start
You followed me?

01:14:29.136 --> 01:14:32.472 position:10% line:83% align:start
Under Mount Hua's Lotus Peak
sits a nest of Phoenixes.

01:14:33.174 --> 01:14:35.042 position:5% line:89% align:start
They are the spirits of fire.

01:14:35.576 --> 01:14:37.511 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Powerful enough to</i>
 <i>destroy the world.</i>

01:14:38.012 --> 01:14:39.714 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>If set free,</i>
 <i>the cosmos would splinter.</i>

01:14:40.848 --> 01:14:43.217 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>The goddess, Nwa gifted</i>
 <i>the lamp to your mother</i>

01:14:43.884 --> 01:14:46.554 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>so she would remain at the peak</i>
 <i>to keep watch over them.</i>

01:14:47.655 --> 01:14:50.024 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>But 12 years ago,</i>
 <i>the Phoenixes grew restless.</i>

01:14:50.558 --> 01:14:52.193 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>The lamp could not</i>
 <i>contain them.</i>

01:14:53.594 --> 01:14:54.895 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>I was sent to help her</i>
 <i>by my master.</i>

01:14:56.197 --> 01:14:58.165 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>But the Phoenixes'</i>
 <i>force was too great.</i>

01:14:59.967 --> 01:15:01.168 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>The lamp shattered.</i>

01:15:01.202 --> 01:15:03.871 position:27% line:83% align:start
[loud thundering]
[shrieking]

01:15:07.608 --> 01:15:10.277 position:16% line:83% align:start
At the last minute, your
mother jumped into the nest

01:15:10.311 --> 01:15:12.680 position:24% line:83% align:start
in order to try and
hold them down herself.

01:15:13.014 --> 01:15:15.282 position:13% line:89% align:start
Brother, look after my son.

01:15:15.950 --> 01:15:16.984 position:41% line:89% align:start
Sister!

01:15:17.918 --> 01:15:19.920 position:16% line:89% align:start
You must seal Lotus Peak.

01:15:21.188 --> 01:15:23.858 position:21% line:89% align:start
[magical thundering]

01:15:24.091 --> 01:15:26.260 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

01:15:29.030 --> 01:15:31.032 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Jian yells]

01:15:31.065 --> 01:15:32.867 position:30% line:89% align:start
[deep rumbling]

01:15:37.271 --> 01:15:39.040 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Jian]
 <i>I drove my ax into the rock.</i>

01:15:39.707 --> 01:15:41.175 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yells]

01:15:41.942 --> 01:15:43.711 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ax booms]

01:15:46.113 --> 01:15:48.983 position:7% line:89% align:start
Thus sealing the Phoenixes in.

01:15:50.217 --> 01:15:51.786 position:24% line:89% align:start
And your Third Eye

01:15:53.054 --> 01:15:54.655 position:21% line:89% align:start
hasn't opened since.

01:16:04.331 --> 01:16:07.601 position:21% line:83% align:start
So she wasn't buried
for marrying a mortal?

01:16:07.802 --> 01:16:09.136 position:19% line:89% align:start
She sacrificed herself?

01:16:12.106 --> 01:16:13.741 position:35% line:89% align:start
Chenxiang,

01:16:13.774 --> 01:16:15.810 position:16% line:83% align:start
your grandmother married
a mortal as well,

01:16:16.143 --> 01:16:17.111 position:16% line:89% align:start
and had me and your mom.

01:16:19.413 --> 01:16:22.216 position:13% line:83% align:start
Because I had been wounded,
I couldn't care for you.

01:16:22.249 --> 01:16:23.884 position:27% line:83% align:start
That's why I took
you to Jin Xia Cave.

01:16:23.918 --> 01:16:25.886 position:27% line:83% align:start
You couldn't even
come to see me?

01:16:25.920 --> 01:16:27.021 position:27% line:89% align:start
You're my uncle!

01:16:29.023 --> 01:16:31.092 position:24% line:89% align:start
[melancholic music]

01:16:31.125 --> 01:16:33.160 position:21% line:83% align:start
My Master forbade me
before you were trained.

01:16:37.264 --> 01:16:38.799 position:16% line:89% align:start
Is he telling the truth?

01:16:38.833 --> 01:16:39.800 position:24% line:89% align:start
Well, grandmother?

01:16:40.201 --> 01:16:41.235 position:27% line:89% align:start
Grandmother?

01:16:42.803 --> 01:16:43.838 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's true.

01:16:44.805 --> 01:16:45.639 position:35% line:89% align:start
All of it.

01:16:47.842 --> 01:16:51.112 position:19% line:83% align:start
Yang Jian, your mother,
Yaoji was my best friend.

01:16:52.746 --> 01:16:54.048 position:21% line:89% align:start
I have another name.

01:16:54.081 --> 01:16:55.049 position:21% line:89% align:start
Goddess of Mount Wu.

01:16:57.685 --> 01:16:59.753 position:16% line:83% align:start
There's more to the story
than what's been told.

01:17:01.856 --> 01:17:02.690 position:35% line:89% align:start
Follow me.

01:17:08.762 --> 01:17:11.232 position:27% line:89% align:start
[wind whistling]

01:17:17.471 --> 01:17:18.305 position:38% line:89% align:start
Mount Hua

01:17:19.707 --> 01:17:21.175 position:30% line:89% align:start
and Lotus Peak.

01:17:21.208 --> 01:17:23.043 position:27% line:89% align:start
See those lights?

01:17:23.077 --> 01:17:24.979 position:13% line:89% align:start
The Phoenixes are agitated.

01:17:25.279 --> 01:17:27.414 position:13% line:89% align:start
And their power is waking.

01:17:27.448 --> 01:17:29.383 position:21% line:83% align:start
My mother is trapped
under that mountain then?

01:17:37.725 --> 01:17:39.260 position:33% line:83% align:start
This was once
Mount Li's beacon tower.

01:17:40.961 --> 01:17:43.164 position:19% line:83% align:start
King You would light it
for his concubine, Bao Si,

01:17:43.197 --> 01:17:44.765 position:24% line:89% align:start
for her amusement.

01:17:45.733 --> 01:17:48.736 position:19% line:83% align:start
The issue was the false
alarms he created.

01:17:49.136 --> 01:17:51.071 position:30% line:83% align:start
And in the end,
his kingdom perished.

01:17:52.439 --> 01:17:54.208 position:30% line:83% align:start
Yet it's always
the woman's fault.

01:17:56.343 --> 01:17:57.378 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yang Jian,

01:17:58.547 --> 01:18:01.348 position:16% line:83% align:start
do you know why you used
the lamp to seal the Phoenixes?

01:18:03.951 --> 01:18:05.452 position:21% line:89% align:start
To save Jin Xia Cave.

01:18:06.521 --> 01:18:08.189 position:24% line:89% align:start
[intriguing music]

01:18:08.222 --> 01:18:10.324 position:27% line:83% align:start
Your master used
the Phoenixes' power

01:18:11.192 --> 01:18:13.260 position:13% line:89% align:start
to keep the cave standing.

01:18:14.228 --> 01:18:16.764 position:7% line:83% align:start
When the Phoenix's break free,
the cave will collapse.

01:18:18.465 --> 01:18:21.735 position:13% line:83% align:start
Keeping them sealed is what
keeps Jin Xia standing.

01:18:21.769 --> 01:18:23.938 position:19% line:83% align:start
That is the true reason
why your master sent you

01:18:23.971 --> 01:18:25.005 position:24% line:89% align:start
to seal them away.

01:18:26.140 --> 01:18:27.474 position:24% line:89% align:start
I don't understand.

01:18:27.509 --> 01:18:29.210 position:21% line:83% align:start
He told me that this
would save lives.

01:18:29.243 --> 01:18:30.411 position:21% line:89% align:start
Prevent destruction.

01:18:30.444 --> 01:18:31.979 position:19% line:83% align:start
He never said anything
about the cave.

01:18:32.213 --> 01:18:33.814 position:16% line:89% align:start
His reasons are selfish.

01:18:37.017 --> 01:18:39.486 position:10% line:83% align:start
Heaven and Earth are ruled by
cycles, and so the Phoenixes

01:18:41.188 --> 01:18:42.156 position:19% line:89% align:start
will surely rise again.

01:18:43.290 --> 01:18:46.160 position:27% line:89% align:start
[low thundering]

01:18:52.132 --> 01:18:54.835 position:27% line:83% align:start
Yang Jian, do you
remember when it was

01:18:54.868 --> 01:18:56.337 position:10% line:89% align:start
that you split the mountain?

01:18:57.071 --> 01:18:58.239 position:16% line:89% align:start
It was back during..

01:18:58.939 --> 01:18:59.974 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:19:00.241 --> 01:19:01.275 position:13% line:89% align:start
the last Great Catastrophe.

01:19:01.543 --> 01:19:02.943 position:27% line:89% align:start
And so the truth

01:19:02.977 --> 01:19:04.979 position:21% line:83% align:start
is he manipulated for
his own selfishness.

01:19:05.547 --> 01:19:06.380 position:24% line:89% align:start
You were his pawn.

01:19:08.949 --> 01:19:11.218 position:16% line:83% align:start
Let us split the mountain
and rescue your mother.

01:19:27.935 --> 01:19:28.969 position:47% line:89% align:start
Hm.

01:19:33.575 --> 01:19:36.377 position:16% line:83% align:start
Wanluo, if this is true,
I want to help.

01:19:36.410 --> 01:19:38.846 position:27% line:83% align:start
But before I do,
would you accompany me

01:19:38.879 --> 01:19:40.047 position:19% line:89% align:start
to confront my Master?

01:19:42.416 --> 01:19:44.519 position:13% line:89% align:start
Chenxiang, you'll come too.

01:19:44.952 --> 01:19:46.353 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'm not going back with you.

01:19:46.920 --> 01:19:48.489 position:24% line:83% align:start
You and the Elders
are all the same.

01:19:49.156 --> 01:19:50.491 position:35% line:89% align:start
Just leave!

01:19:50.924 --> 01:19:52.126 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'll do it.

01:19:52.159 --> 01:19:52.993 position:35% line:89% align:start
Chenxiang!

01:19:53.394 --> 01:19:55.262 position:27% line:89% align:start
[magic whirring]

01:19:55.630 --> 01:19:58.399 position:10% line:83% align:start
Knowing everything, you still
want to run to your Master.

01:20:06.407 --> 01:20:08.242 position:30% line:83% align:start
[mirror clangs]
[Jian panting]

01:20:08.275 --> 01:20:10.177 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

01:20:11.478 --> 01:20:12.313 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

01:20:15.249 --> 01:20:16.450 position:27% line:89% align:start
[water splashing]

01:20:24.892 --> 01:20:26.493 position:30% line:89% align:start
[vase shatters]

01:20:26.528 --> 01:20:29.196 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

01:20:51.553 --> 01:20:52.386 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Wanluo gasps]
[Jian grunts]

01:21:03.364 --> 01:21:05.032 position:24% line:89% align:start
Sorry, Goddess Wu.

01:21:05.366 --> 01:21:07.301 position:7% line:89% align:start
I fear if Chenxiang stays here,

01:21:07.702 --> 01:21:09.470 position:21% line:83% align:start
he'll share the same
fate as Shen Gongbao.

01:21:09.503 --> 01:21:10.971 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

01:21:11.171 --> 01:21:13.040 position:30% line:89% align:start
[somber music]

01:21:14.041 --> 01:21:14.942 position:21% line:89% align:start
What are you saying?

01:21:17.111 --> 01:21:19.446 position:10% line:83% align:start
When we last saw each other,
you cast a spell on me.

01:21:20.347 --> 01:21:21.549 position:19% line:83% align:start
While I was enchanted,
I had a dream.

01:21:22.282 --> 01:21:24.318 position:16% line:89% align:start
Jian, split the mountain.

01:21:24.552 --> 01:21:25.620 position:19% line:89% align:start
That wasn't my mother.

01:21:26.954 --> 01:21:29.524 position:5% line:89% align:start
It was you, Goddess of Mount Wu.

01:21:31.091 --> 01:21:34.194 position:5% line:83% align:start
Using dreams to confuse people
is your signature skill.

01:21:37.064 --> 01:21:39.400 position:19% line:83% align:start
The Second Elder wasn't
killed by Chenxiang,

01:21:40.401 --> 01:21:41.435 position:27% line:89% align:start
nor Shen Gongbao.

01:21:43.036 --> 01:21:45.573 position:21% line:83% align:start
The lacerations I saw
resembled a silken web.

01:21:47.441 --> 01:21:50.277 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>When I found Shen Gongbao,</i>
 <i>he was still alive.</i>

01:21:50.712 --> 01:21:52.547 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>He had been injured</i>
 <i>by a powerful weapon.</i>

01:21:53.748 --> 01:21:55.550 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>What really killed him</i>

01:21:55.583 --> 01:21:57.184 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>were the wounds</i>
 <i>from a silken web.</i>

01:21:59.286 --> 01:22:02.256 position:16% line:83% align:start
And just now you tried to
attack me with a silken web.

01:22:04.191 --> 01:22:07.027 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>That's when I was reminded</i>
 <i>that your special magic weapon</i>

01:22:07.060 --> 01:22:08.195 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>is a web.</i>

01:22:08.228 --> 01:22:10.464 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>The Second Elder</i>
 <i>and Shen Gongbao</i>

01:22:12.567 --> 01:22:14.301 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>were both murdered by you.</i>

01:22:17.137 --> 01:22:19.039 position:30% line:89% align:start
[panting] You--

01:22:26.514 --> 01:22:27.549 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's true.

01:22:28.282 --> 01:22:29.082 position:35% line:89% align:start
All of it.

01:22:30.552 --> 01:22:31.653 position:13% line:89% align:start
Why did you have to do it?

01:22:32.754 --> 01:22:35.590 position:19% line:83% align:start
If I hadn't, you never
would've left Jin Xia Cave.

01:22:37.057 --> 01:22:38.959 position:21% line:83% align:start
Shen Gongbao's death
was unfortunate.

01:22:39.527 --> 01:22:40.528 position:16% line:89% align:start
We were working together,

01:22:41.596 --> 01:22:43.197 position:7% line:89% align:start
but when I found him like that,

01:22:43.464 --> 01:22:45.199 position:13% line:89% align:start
I couldn't let him suffer,

01:22:45.667 --> 01:22:47.234 position:7% line:89% align:start
so I put him out of his misery.

01:22:48.135 --> 01:22:49.671 position:5% line:89% align:start
I still don't understand why.

01:22:50.170 --> 01:22:53.474 position:13% line:83% align:start
Chenxiang, everything I did
was to split the mountain

01:22:53.508 --> 01:22:54.642 position:21% line:89% align:start
and save your mother.

01:22:55.342 --> 01:22:56.376 position:27% line:89% align:start
Unlike Yang Jian.

01:22:58.513 --> 01:23:00.648 position:19% line:83% align:start
Whatever your reasons,
you can't just kill others.

01:23:05.620 --> 01:23:08.656 position:30% line:89% align:start
[lamp whirring]

01:23:10.491 --> 01:23:13.260 position:41% line:89% align:start
Enough!

01:23:14.629 --> 01:23:17.297 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

01:23:24.539 --> 01:23:26.541 position:27% line:89% align:start
[chains thumping]

01:23:54.769 --> 01:23:57.772 position:24% line:89% align:start
[harmonica playing]

01:24:26.834 --> 01:24:27.835 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

01:24:39.914 --> 01:24:41.549 position:21% line:89% align:start
[gasps] Where's my--?

01:24:42.416 --> 01:24:43.450 position:33% line:89% align:start
Give it back!

01:24:46.453 --> 01:24:48.188 position:27% line:89% align:start
Oh. I removed it.

01:24:48.221 --> 01:24:49.323 position:13% line:89% align:start
It was burning your wrist.

01:24:51.826 --> 01:24:53.628 position:30% line:83% align:start
I've never been
able to take it off.

01:24:53.661 --> 01:24:54.629 position:19% line:89% align:start
It's always been there.

01:24:55.462 --> 01:24:56.496 position:27% line:89% align:start
How'd you do it?

01:24:57.665 --> 01:24:58.700 position:33% line:89% align:start
I don't know.

01:24:59.867 --> 01:25:01.401 position:24% line:83% align:start
Maybe it's because
I'm your uncle.

01:25:02.537 --> 01:25:04.706 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gentle music]

01:25:04.739 --> 01:25:07.341 position:24% line:83% align:start
She gave this to me
before she made the leap.

01:25:08.843 --> 01:25:10.612 position:7% line:89% align:start
She wove it from her own hair.

01:25:10.645 --> 01:25:12.245 position:7% line:89% align:start
Told me to give it to her son.

01:25:19.687 --> 01:25:20.788 position:19% line:89% align:start
The bracelet is a wick.

01:25:22.222 --> 01:25:23.390 position:16% line:89% align:start
To light the Lotus Lamp.

01:25:25.392 --> 01:25:27.629 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

01:25:32.499 --> 01:25:34.669 position:16% line:89% align:start
I just miss her so much.

01:25:39.674 --> 01:25:42.810 position:10% line:89% align:start
[distant ominous screeching]

01:25:43.477 --> 01:25:44.612 position:7% line:89% align:start
I'll go to Mount Hua with you.

01:25:44.646 --> 01:25:46.914 position:13% line:89% align:start
[gentle adventurous music]

01:25:47.782 --> 01:25:49.216 position:24% line:83% align:start
Then we can get to
the bottom of this.

01:25:57.925 --> 01:26:00.561 position:19% line:89% align:start
[upbeat mystical music]

01:26:12.740 --> 01:26:13.975 position:21% line:5% align:start
[singing in Mandarin]

01:26:14.008 --> 01:26:15.543 position:24% line:5% align:start
Nine-Turns Kungfu?

01:26:44.539 --> 01:26:45.640 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

01:26:45.673 --> 01:26:47.240 position:38% line:83% align:start
[shouts]
[water splashing]

01:26:50.477 --> 01:26:53.748 position:19% line:5% align:start
[upbeat mystical music]
[singing in Mandarin]

01:27:01.421 --> 01:27:02.489 position:38% line:5% align:start
[shouts]

01:27:07.662 --> 01:27:08.730 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yells]

01:27:19.807 --> 01:27:22.342 position:33% line:89% align:start
[soft music]

01:27:29.016 --> 01:27:32.419 position:19% line:89% align:start
[upbeat mystical music]

01:27:36.356 --> 01:27:38.526 position:24% line:89% align:start
[soldiers grunting]

01:27:51.739 --> 01:27:54.008 position:27% line:5% align:start
[wind whistling]

01:28:07.420 --> 01:28:08.055 position:33% line:89% align:start
You're home.

01:28:09.891 --> 01:28:10.925 position:27% line:89% align:start
I was born here.

01:28:15.129 --> 01:28:17.665 position:33% line:89% align:start
[soft music]

01:28:42.389 --> 01:28:44.457 position:27% line:89% align:start
[chimes ringing]

01:29:03.845 --> 01:29:06.614 position:27% line:89% align:start
[chimes ringing]

01:29:08.616 --> 01:29:10.818 position:30% line:89% align:start
[baby laughing]

01:29:18.960 --> 01:29:21.394 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ethereal music]

01:29:22.830 --> 01:29:24.799 position:30% line:89% align:start
[baby laughing]

01:29:29.871 --> 01:29:30.905 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mother.

01:29:38.212 --> 01:29:40.014 position:24% line:89% align:start
[melancholic music]

01:29:48.689 --> 01:29:49.891 position:38% line:89% align:start
Let's go.

01:29:52.660 --> 01:29:54.996 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

01:30:08.910 --> 01:30:10.945 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Jian coughing]

01:30:17.718 --> 01:30:19.921 position:30% line:89% align:start
[low rumbling]

01:30:32.566 --> 01:30:34.869 position:27% line:89% align:start
[winds whistling]

01:30:36.070 --> 01:30:38.973 position:27% line:89% align:start
[low tense music]

01:30:45.112 --> 01:30:46.814 position:30% line:83% align:start
This carving is
the Order of the Gods.

01:30:48.115 --> 01:30:49.650 position:10% line:89% align:start
How did I not notice before?

01:30:50.785 --> 01:30:53.453 position:16% line:83% align:start
All this while, the Order
was carved on Mount Hua.

01:30:54.822 --> 01:30:57.558 position:30% line:89% align:start
[deep rumbling]

01:31:11.639 --> 01:31:15.109 position:35% line:83% align:start
[rumbling]
[screeching]

01:31:19.113 --> 01:31:21.148 position:13% line:89% align:start
And there's the ax I used.

01:31:21.182 --> 01:31:23.684 position:24% line:83% align:start
So it's sealing the
peak you split open?

01:31:25.953 --> 01:31:27.154 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Jian] Not completely.

01:31:27.188 --> 01:31:29.056 position:10% line:89% align:start
Their energy is spilling out.

01:31:29.090 --> 01:31:30.091 position:13% line:89% align:start
You can see it right there.

01:31:34.962 --> 01:31:37.131 position:33% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

01:31:57.351 --> 01:31:59.220 position:13% line:89% align:start
Yang Jian, you have to go.

01:32:00.087 --> 01:32:02.089 position:33% line:89% align:start
[struggling]

01:32:04.658 --> 01:32:05.693 position:30% line:89% align:start
Celestial rope?

01:32:05.893 --> 01:32:07.094 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Chenxiang, run!
-Huh?

01:32:08.796 --> 01:32:11.065 position:33% line:89% align:start
[shattering]

01:32:15.903 --> 01:32:17.171 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screaming]

01:32:18.839 --> 01:32:19.874 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uncle!

01:32:19.907 --> 01:32:21.942 position:30% line:89% align:start
[deep rumbling]

01:32:22.276 --> 01:32:24.712 position:30% line:89% align:start
[intense music]

01:32:46.700 --> 01:32:49.136 position:24% line:89% align:start
[stones shattering]

01:32:50.738 --> 01:32:51.872 position:30% line:89% align:start
[both grunting]

01:32:52.406 --> 01:32:54.075 position:30% line:89% align:start
[lute playing]

01:32:55.776 --> 01:32:57.912 position:21% line:83% align:start
Looks like we finally
caught you, traitor.

01:32:59.113 --> 01:33:02.316 position:19% line:83% align:start
This Thai Chi scroll is
such a marvelous treasure, no?

01:33:03.417 --> 01:33:06.287 position:30% line:83% align:start
With one hand,
your fears, it will quell.

01:33:06.320 --> 01:33:09.156 position:19% line:83% align:start
And with the other, it
manifests your deepest desires

01:33:09.190 --> 01:33:10.224 position:38% line:89% align:start
as well.

01:33:11.725 --> 01:33:13.861 position:27% line:83% align:start
The awesome power
of this scroll

01:33:13.894 --> 01:33:16.230 position:24% line:83% align:start
should be enough to
keep Yang Jian trapped.

01:33:19.667 --> 01:33:20.601 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:33:21.035 --> 01:33:23.771 position:27% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

01:33:27.942 --> 01:33:29.210 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Jian yelling]

01:33:29.243 --> 01:33:32.113 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

01:33:37.718 --> 01:33:40.254 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screaming]

01:33:42.857 --> 01:33:43.924 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Mother] Jian.

01:33:50.431 --> 01:33:51.699 position:44% line:89% align:start
Jian.

01:33:51.732 --> 01:33:53.267 position:35% line:89% align:start
[rumbling]

01:33:53.968 --> 01:33:55.035 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mother.

01:33:55.069 --> 01:33:56.103 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mother!

01:33:56.837 --> 01:33:57.972 position:33% line:89% align:start
[door slams]

01:33:58.906 --> 01:34:00.841 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screaming]

01:34:01.342 --> 01:34:03.911 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Mother]
 <i>Jian, split the mountain.</i>

01:34:04.311 --> 01:34:06.714 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Jian yells]
[ax smashes]

01:34:08.916 --> 01:34:10.951 position:33% line:89% align:start
[screeching]

01:34:12.419 --> 01:34:14.955 position:35% line:89% align:start
[shouting]

01:34:28.035 --> 01:34:28.869 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Mother] Jian.

01:34:29.937 --> 01:34:31.172 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mother?

01:34:31.205 --> 01:34:32.273 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mother?

01:34:32.306 --> 01:34:34.675 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ethereal music]

01:34:36.343 --> 01:34:37.845 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Mother] <i>Jian.</i>

01:34:37.878 --> 01:34:38.712 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Jian] Mother.

01:34:39.914 --> 01:34:42.049 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Mother]
 <i>Mount Hua is open.</i>

01:34:42.082 --> 01:34:43.083 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>It's time for me to go.</i>

01:34:44.251 --> 01:34:45.252 position:38% line:89% align:start
But why?

01:34:46.387 --> 01:34:47.922 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Mother]
 <i>Because it is fated.</i>

01:34:49.023 --> 01:34:50.357 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>The women in our family</i>

01:34:50.925 --> 01:34:53.427 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>are destined to hold down</i>
 <i>the mountain.</i>

01:34:53.460 --> 01:34:55.664 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>To secure peace in the world.</i>

01:34:56.063 --> 01:34:57.164 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sobs]

01:35:00.901 --> 01:35:01.869 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mother.

01:35:03.070 --> 01:35:03.904 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Mother] <i>Jian,</i>

01:35:05.172 --> 01:35:06.340 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>you needn't cry.</i>

01:35:07.808 --> 01:35:08.842 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>Look.</i>

01:35:09.843 --> 01:35:11.145 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>Do you see these sparks?</i>

01:35:12.379 --> 01:35:13.247 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>They're all me.</i>

01:35:15.182 --> 01:35:16.784 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>All things live forever.</i>

01:35:17.885 --> 01:35:20.020 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>And so I will live on</i>
 <i>in all things.</i>

01:35:20.555 --> 01:35:21.956 position:27% line:83% align:start
-[Jian sobs] No.
-[Mother] <i>If you miss me,</i>

01:35:23.123 --> 01:35:25.459 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>look to the lamps that burn</i>
 <i>in every window.</i>

01:35:25.893 --> 01:35:27.394 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Mother. [sniffles]
 <i>-And you'll see me there.</i>

01:35:28.195 --> 01:35:29.964 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mother!

01:35:29.997 --> 01:35:31.498 position:30% line:89% align:start
[fire roaring]

01:35:31.533 --> 01:35:32.766 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mother!

01:35:32.800 --> 01:35:33.867 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

01:35:34.401 --> 01:35:36.070 position:13% line:89% align:start
I already split Mount Tao!

01:35:36.103 --> 01:35:37.171 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mother!

01:35:37.204 --> 01:35:38.372 position:30% line:89% align:start
Where are you?

01:35:39.106 --> 01:35:40.741 position:27% line:89% align:start
[shouts, grunts]

01:35:41.842 --> 01:35:43.911 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Master]
You must secure Mount Hua.

01:35:44.378 --> 01:35:45.779 position:16% line:89% align:start
I must secure Mount Hua.

01:35:46.146 --> 01:35:48.115 position:24% line:89% align:start
Restore the peace.

01:35:48.148 --> 01:35:49.350 position:21% line:89% align:start
To restore the peace.

01:35:50.050 --> 01:35:51.151 position:27% line:89% align:start
Secure Mount Hua.

01:35:52.119 --> 01:35:54.888 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>-Brother, look after my son.</i>
-No!

01:35:57.858 --> 01:36:00.928 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Jian groaning]

01:36:00.961 --> 01:36:02.496 position:38% line:89% align:start
[screams]

01:36:03.097 --> 01:36:04.898 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ax thundering]

01:36:07.334 --> 01:36:10.104 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Jian yelling]

01:36:16.143 --> 01:36:18.279 position:27% line:89% align:start
[cranes calling]

01:36:23.417 --> 01:36:25.019 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Master] How is your eye?

01:36:25.319 --> 01:36:27.087 position:19% line:89% align:start
Is it still closed off?

01:36:27.121 --> 01:36:28.523 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

01:36:32.459 --> 01:36:33.294 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes.

01:36:35.863 --> 01:36:40.000 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Master] 12 years ago when you
went and sealed off Lotus Peak,

01:36:42.036 --> 01:36:45.172 position:7% line:89% align:start
and yet the unrest carries on.

01:36:45.540 --> 01:36:49.943 position:7% line:83% align:start
I thought things would change,
but I was wrong in the end.

01:36:50.344 --> 01:36:52.580 position:27% line:83% align:start
Sooner or later,
catastrophe will return.

01:36:52.980 --> 01:36:54.315 position:30% line:89% align:start
[uneasy music]

01:36:54.348 --> 01:36:55.382 position:41% line:89% align:start
Master?

01:36:57.451 --> 01:37:01.188 position:13% line:83% align:start
[voice slowing, distorting]
It is how to restore order.

01:37:06.060 --> 01:37:09.830 position:13% line:83% align:start
And only then, the heavens
will begin to heal.

01:37:15.469 --> 01:37:18.172 position:30% line:89% align:start
[deep rumbling]

01:37:30.150 --> 01:37:33.320 position:27% line:83% align:start
[music continues]
[groaning]

01:37:45.165 --> 01:37:46.200 position:41% line:89% align:start
Master.

01:37:49.537 --> 01:37:51.071 position:10% line:89% align:start
This is the Thai Chi scroll.

01:37:51.105 --> 01:37:53.140 position:30% line:83% align:start
You're the one
holding me in here?

01:37:54.609 --> 01:37:57.945 position:19% line:83% align:start
[sighs] You were always
my greatest student.

01:37:58.979 --> 01:38:01.382 position:13% line:83% align:start
I am impressed that you're
able to combat the effects

01:38:01.415 --> 01:38:02.950 position:19% line:89% align:start
of the scroll's magic.

01:38:03.618 --> 01:38:06.053 position:30% line:83% align:start
Wait a minute,
I remember the story.

01:38:07.221 --> 01:38:08.989 position:16% line:83% align:start
It was Yin Hong's master
who turned his apprentice

01:38:09.022 --> 01:38:10.391 position:38% line:89% align:start
to ashes.

01:38:11.959 --> 01:38:13.227 position:41% line:89% align:start
Master.

01:38:13.260 --> 01:38:14.428 position:16% line:89% align:start
What crime did I commit?

01:38:16.029 --> 01:38:17.599 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yang Jian,

01:38:18.600 --> 01:38:21.435 position:16% line:83% align:start
I can not allow Chenxiang
to split Mount Hua.

01:38:21.468 --> 01:38:22.503 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's all...

01:38:23.237 --> 01:38:24.505 position:16% line:89% align:start
to protect Jin Xia Cave.

01:38:26.306 --> 01:38:27.975 position:27% line:89% align:start
So you know now.

01:38:29.376 --> 01:38:31.979 position:30% line:83% align:start
We cannot allow
the cave to fall.

01:38:32.279 --> 01:38:35.949 position:10% line:83% align:start
Everything I've done has been
to preserve Jin Xia Cave.

01:38:35.983 --> 01:38:38.118 position:7% line:89% align:start
Why can't you understand that?

01:38:38.152 --> 01:38:39.219 position:38% line:89% align:start
So then,

01:38:40.187 --> 01:38:41.955 position:24% line:83% align:start
my sister is still
locked under Mount Hua.

01:38:41.989 --> 01:38:43.390 position:19% line:89% align:start
Because it's her fate!

01:38:44.458 --> 01:38:46.427 position:24% line:89% align:start
[melancholic music]

01:38:49.096 --> 01:38:50.532 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yang Jian,

01:38:51.098 --> 01:38:54.736 position:30% line:83% align:start
you do not know
the Yang family curse.

01:38:54.769 --> 01:38:58.238 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>It lies between</i>
 <i>mothers and sons.</i>

01:38:58.272 --> 01:39:02.176 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>You are linked by fate to</i>
 <i>the cycle of catastrophe.</i>

01:39:02.209 --> 01:39:04.746 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>The mothers must hold</i>
 <i>down the mountains</i>

01:39:04.779 --> 01:39:07.715 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>for the sake of</i>
 <i>preserving peace,</i>

01:39:07.749 --> 01:39:12.119 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>and the sons will always</i>
 <i>try to save their mothers</i>

01:39:12.152 --> 01:39:14.622 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>by splitting the mountains.</i>

01:39:14.656 --> 01:39:18.358 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>But what you don't know</i>
 <i>is if the mountain is split</i>

01:39:18.392 --> 01:39:22.630 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>and the Phoenixes are freed,</i>
 <i>the cave will collapse.</i>

01:39:22.664 --> 01:39:27.401 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Chaos and catastrophe will</i>
 <i>return just as it did before.</i>

01:39:27.769 --> 01:39:30.504 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>And only after the dust settles</i>

01:39:31.138 --> 01:39:34.441 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>will peace return</i>
 <i>to heaven once more.</i>

01:39:35.476 --> 01:39:37.077 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasping]

01:39:37.110 --> 01:39:38.011 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Master] My boy,

01:39:39.514 --> 01:39:40.548 position:44% line:89% align:start
Jian,

01:39:42.750 --> 01:39:46.320 position:27% line:83% align:start
the last to split
Mount Hua was you.

01:39:47.622 --> 01:39:51.626 position:35% line:83% align:start
This round,
it's Chenxiang's turn.

01:39:55.429 --> 01:39:57.532 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Jian laughing]

01:40:00.334 --> 01:40:01.368 position:41% line:89% align:start
Master.

01:40:02.604 --> 01:40:04.171 position:10% line:89% align:start
You took me in as an orphan.

01:40:05.372 --> 01:40:08.075 position:16% line:83% align:start
Raised me as one of
your holy disciples.

01:40:08.510 --> 01:40:10.210 position:24% line:83% align:start
Taught me all sorts
of different magic.

01:40:11.679 --> 01:40:13.681 position:5% line:89% align:start
And all for the purpose of using

01:40:13.715 --> 01:40:15.550 position:21% line:83% align:start
so that I could split
Mount Tao one day.

01:40:17.719 --> 01:40:20.755 position:21% line:83% align:start
When you looked after
Chenxiang, you hid his powers,

01:40:20.788 --> 01:40:23.658 position:30% line:83% align:start
his origins and
everything from him.

01:40:23.691 --> 01:40:25.359 position:19% line:83% align:start
But this time it was to
keep him from splitting

01:40:25.392 --> 01:40:26.460 position:33% line:89% align:start
the mountain.

01:40:26.493 --> 01:40:27.529 position:38% line:89% align:start
Correct.

01:40:28.428 --> 01:40:30.397 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yang Jian,

01:40:30.430 --> 01:40:32.667 position:10% line:89% align:start
I am trying to preserve peace

01:40:32.700 --> 01:40:35.235 position:19% line:83% align:start
just as your mother did
before me.

01:40:36.203 --> 01:40:39.206 position:16% line:83% align:start
As long as the Phoenixes
remain under the mountain,

01:40:39.239 --> 01:40:41.275 position:13% line:89% align:start
the cave will also remain.

01:40:42.777 --> 01:40:45.547 position:21% line:83% align:start
Your precious cave is
destined to collapse.

01:40:45.580 --> 01:40:46.748 position:7% line:89% align:start
The longer they're suppressed,

01:40:46.781 --> 01:40:48.348 position:7% line:89% align:start
the more powerful they'll grow.

01:40:48.382 --> 01:40:50.117 position:24% line:83% align:start
When they're free,
they'll destroy the world.

01:40:50.885 --> 01:40:53.521 position:10% line:83% align:start
And protecting Jin Xia Cave,
it's not for the greater good,

01:40:53.555 --> 01:40:55.155 position:16% line:89% align:start
it's for selfish reasons!

01:40:55.557 --> 01:40:57.659 position:21% line:89% align:start
That cave is my life!

01:40:57.692 --> 01:41:00.762 position:16% line:83% align:start
The life of all disciples
who've passed through it.

01:41:00.795 --> 01:41:02.730 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's glory belongs to all.

01:41:03.565 --> 01:41:06.634 position:5% line:89% align:start
Harm to it is harm to all.

01:41:08.570 --> 01:41:12.472 position:24% line:83% align:start
Even if I'm wrong,
then I'll be wrong to the end.

01:41:14.241 --> 01:41:16.476 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Jian laughs]

01:41:20.480 --> 01:41:21.583 position:41% line:89% align:start
Master,

01:41:23.350 --> 01:41:26.320 position:16% line:83% align:start
the disciples you trained
were only a means to an end.

01:41:27.755 --> 01:41:28.388 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yang Jian,

01:41:29.891 --> 01:41:31.626 position:10% line:89% align:start
I never wanted to see you go.

01:41:33.160 --> 01:41:35.195 position:24% line:83% align:start
But for the sake of
everything that is dear,

01:41:36.263 --> 01:41:38.432 position:10% line:89% align:start
you shall be turned to dust.

01:41:39.266 --> 01:41:40.768 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

01:41:44.304 --> 01:41:46.340 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Chan groaning]
[Chenxiang grunting]

01:41:47.809 --> 01:41:49.309 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Chenxiang yells]

01:41:51.779 --> 01:41:53.548 position:27% line:89% align:start
[glass shatters]

01:41:53.915 --> 01:41:56.149 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yelling]

01:41:57.619 --> 01:41:59.821 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

01:42:02.857 --> 01:42:05.526 position:24% line:89% align:start
[low ominous music]

01:42:18.338 --> 01:42:20.942 position:33% line:83% align:start
The celestial
rope and the scroll,

01:42:20.975 --> 01:42:24.812 position:10% line:83% align:start
both of these weapons belong
to the Masters who came before.

01:42:25.546 --> 01:42:27.782 position:13% line:89% align:start
We all want the same goal,

01:42:27.815 --> 01:42:30.384 position:24% line:83% align:start
to keep chaos from
returning to the world.

01:42:32.419 --> 01:42:34.589 position:33% line:89% align:start
[lute strums]

01:42:37.592 --> 01:42:39.426 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whooshing]

01:42:44.666 --> 01:42:47.535 position:27% line:89% align:start
[lute strumming]

01:42:56.711 --> 01:42:57.879 position:35% line:89% align:start
Chenxiang!

01:42:58.513 --> 01:43:00.648 position:24% line:83% align:start
Chenxiang, protect
yourself with the lamp!

01:43:05.553 --> 01:43:10.357 position:30% line:83% align:start
[blade clashes]
[drums beating]

01:43:11.693 --> 01:43:13.460 position:27% line:89% align:start
Huh? It can't be!

01:43:14.529 --> 01:43:16.698 position:27% line:89% align:start
[drums continue]

01:43:19.433 --> 01:43:21.435 position:30% line:89% align:start
[low rumbling]

01:43:23.738 --> 01:43:27.207 position:38% line:83% align:start
[grunts]
[lute playing]

01:43:30.545 --> 01:43:31.746 position:27% line:89% align:start
[blades clashing]

01:43:37.317 --> 01:43:38.820 position:21% line:83% align:start
Your Nine-Turns form
is getting better.

01:43:44.357 --> 01:43:46.493 position:27% line:89% align:start
[lute strumming]

01:43:46.861 --> 01:43:49.630 position:27% line:89% align:start
[blades clanging]

01:43:58.072 --> 01:44:01.374 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Phoenix screeching]

01:44:13.054 --> 01:44:15.056 position:33% line:83% align:start
The Phoenix's
power is so great

01:44:15.089 --> 01:44:16.758 position:21% line:83% align:start
it's tearing through
the Thai Chi scroll.

01:44:22.029 --> 01:44:24.799 position:21% line:89% align:start
[contemplative music]

01:44:34.742 --> 01:44:37.011 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

01:44:49.690 --> 01:44:54.695 position:24% line:89% align:start
[harmonica playing]

01:44:57.899 --> 01:44:58.933 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

01:45:00.134 --> 01:45:02.837 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

01:45:17.819 --> 01:45:20.655 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Phoenix screeching]

01:45:27.595 --> 01:45:29.063 position:35% line:89% align:start
No, uncle!

01:45:29.897 --> 01:45:32.700 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whooshing]

01:45:40.675 --> 01:45:43.945 position:24% line:89% align:start
[light shimmering]

01:45:43.978 --> 01:45:45.746 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Jian yelling]

01:45:48.616 --> 01:45:50.952 position:16% line:83% align:start
He's using the Phoenixes
to open his Third Eye!

01:45:52.620 --> 01:45:54.789 position:30% line:89% align:start
[driving music]

01:45:55.455 --> 01:45:56.958 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screaming]

01:46:08.703 --> 01:46:12.607 position:24% line:83% align:start
I won't let us pay
for your mistakes.

01:46:12.640 --> 01:46:15.142 position:33% line:89% align:start
[epic music]

01:46:19.513 --> 01:46:20.848 position:27% line:83% align:start
Heaven and Earth,
I rise to thee!

01:46:40.902 --> 01:46:43.037 position:27% line:89% align:start
[deep thundering]

01:47:04.992 --> 01:47:07.061 position:19% line:89% align:start
Fine. We will stop him.

01:47:07.762 --> 01:47:10.965 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

01:47:19.807 --> 01:47:21.142 position:27% line:89% align:start
[lute strumming]

01:47:22.910 --> 01:47:24.245 position:30% line:89% align:start
[bells ringing]

01:47:24.278 --> 01:47:26.013 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whooshing]

01:47:59.280 --> 01:48:03.117 position:27% line:83% align:start
[sword rumbling]
[driving music]

01:48:08.255 --> 01:48:10.524 position:30% line:89% align:start
[loud crashing]

01:48:17.865 --> 01:48:20.601 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

01:48:21.936 --> 01:48:24.171 position:27% line:89% align:start
[music continues]

01:48:28.075 --> 01:48:30.044 position:35% line:89% align:start
[rumbling]

01:48:33.914 --> 01:48:36.050 position:33% line:89% align:start
[epic music]

01:48:39.954 --> 01:48:42.690 position:27% line:89% align:start
[rocks crumbling]

01:48:42.957 --> 01:48:45.559 position:33% line:89% align:start
[screeching]

01:48:52.233 --> 01:48:55.569 position:30% line:83% align:start
Master, what my
mother was protecting

01:48:56.137 --> 01:48:58.339 position:13% line:89% align:start
